Description:
Highlights:
1.- Instant Set-up: The easy set-up requires only a simple maneuver. With the carry bag open, pull the handles on both sides to get this family tent up and standing. The speedy-quick prep saves precious time for the rest of what you have planned for your trip..
2.- Mesh Wall: Stay cool and comfortable with the big mesh walls on this pop up tent. The highly breathable design allows tons of airflow and ventilation. As a bonus, get a full view of the beautiful nature around you. Maybe you'll catch some stars. In the summer, you'll thank the draft coming in..
3.- Dry and Comfortable: The surface is waterproof, allowing up to 3,000 mm of rainwater to cover your needs in case of bad weather. The rainfly adds an extra layer of protection from rain and wind, while with vents to provide ventilation in hot weather..
4.- Portable: This portable backpacking tent fits in a travel bag you can pack it easily in the trunk of a car on-the-go. The duffle features double straps for lifting it easily and comfortably..

Details:

Give yourself the breathable and cool night experience with a big mesh wall to look up at the stars or the tree line. For protection, a 3,000 mm waterproof index offers extra certainty that you can stay dry. The instant design makes this an ultra-easy camp tent, adults, and all camp lovers alike to set it up and get their day started, allowing them to save time with a simple pull of two sides to get the sleep situation standing. 1.The chair is made of high-quality steel pipe, making it lightweight and easy to carry, while also providing excellent support for up to 400lbs.The chair's fabric is made of durable materials and that can withstand the elements, ensuring that it will last for many outdoor activities to come. 4.No installation required.The chair can be easily folded down , making it easy to transport to and from your destination.

Category: Outdoor>>Camping & Hiking>>Sleeping Bags & Camp Bedding>>Sleeping Bags
Product Name: Lightweight Sleeping Bag for Backpacking, Hiking, Waterproof Compact Envelope Sleeping Bag for Cold & Warm Weather, Green
Description:
Details:

Introductions:
Experience the perfect balance of comfort and portability with this ultralight sleeping bag, designed for outdoor enthusiasts and casual campers alike. Crafted from a high-quality and durable 190T polyester shell, this envelope-style bag stands up to years of rugged use while remaining soft against the skin. It offers exceptional versatility, making it an ideal choice for backpacking, hiking, RV trips, or even crashing on a friend's couch. The waterproof outer shell ensures moisture stays out, keeping you dry and cozy throughout the night. With a weight of just 2.1 lbs, it is incredibly easy to carry without adding unnecessary bulk to your pack. Whether you are camping in the mountains or lounging in the backyard, this sleeping bag provides the warmth and reliability needed for a restful sleep in temperatures ranging from 42 to 68 °F.
Features:
1. High-Quality Durable Material: Constructed with a premium 190T polyester shell, this sleeping bag is built to withstand years of regular use. The waterproof outer layer offers excellent protection against moisture, ensuring a dry and comfortable experience during your outdoor adventures or indoor stays.
2. Optimal Temperature Control: Designed for versatility, this backpacking sleeping bag is suitable for a temperature range of 42 to 68 °F. It features an adjustable drawstring that allows you to tighten the bag around your neck, preserving body heat and providing extra warmth in colder weather.
3. Ultralight and Portable Design: Weighing only 2.1 lbs, this sleeping bag achieves the perfect balance of performance and lightweight convenience. It is specifically engineered for hiking and backpacking, making it easy to transport to the mountains, beach, or carry in your car and RV without weighing you down.
4. Secure and Accessible Usage: The bag is equipped with a smooth zipper mechanism secured with a velcro strap to prevent accidental opening while you sleep. This user-friendly design ensures you stay snug throughout the night, whether you are sleeping at the office, in the backyard, or at a campsite.
5. Easy Maintenance and Cleaning: Keeping your gear fresh is effortless as the waterproof shell can be easily wiped clean with a damp cloth to remove surface dirt. For deeper cleaning after heavy soilage, the sleeping bag is fully machine washable, ensuring long-lasting hygiene and durability for every trip.
Specifications:
1. Dimensions: (74.8 x 29.5) in / (190 x 75) cm
2. Weight: 2.1 lbs
3. Temperature Range: 42-68 °F
Package Includes:
1 x Sleeping Bag

Description:
Highlights:
1.Accommodates 2 Adults + 1 Child: The triangular rooftop tent features inflatable poles for easy setup, quickly transforming into a spacious interior that can accommodate 2 adults and 1 child. Suitable for Jeep, SUV, and truck models with a roof weight capacity 600 lbs, it's an ideal choice for family outdoor adventures.
2.Waterproof & UV Protection: The fabric is made from high-density polyester-cotton with a waterproof rating of 1500MM, and features a PU coating for UV protection and insulation. It offers maximum durability and protection in various weather conditions. Note: Avoid use in extreme weather conditions.
3.Wind-Resistant & Sturdy Support Poles: The reinforced ABS hard shell and stainless steel support poles robustly uphold the tent, with wind resistance up to Level 7. When folded, the tent can be secured with locks to prevent it from being lifted by the wind.
4.Enhanced Comfort Inside: Enjoy greater comfort during outdoor camping or overnight stays. The tent features multiple ventilation points, breathable mesh window, and a thick, non-deforming foam mattress for added comfort. It also includes an LED light for easy navigation at night.
5.7.5 FT Telescoping Ladder: Comes with a 7-section aluminum telescoping ladder with a maximum load capacity of 330 lbs, making it easy to enter the tent. The ladder's length is adjustable, extending up to 7.5 ft / 2.3 m and shortening to 2.4 inches / 720 mm to fit different vehicle heights.

Details:
A Mobile Home on The Rooftop of Your Jeep This rooftop tent is designed for families who love outdoor adventures. It offers a spacious space that accommodates 2 adults and 1 child, with doors and windows that provide expansive views and allow you to fully enjoy the great trip. The durable tent will last for many adventures to come. Made from high-density polyester fabric with a waterproof rating of 1500MM, featuring reinforced seams for enhanced waterproofing, this tent ensures you won't have to worry about weather changes during outdoor use. Note: Avoid use in extreme weather conditions such as snowstorms or heavy rain. Equipped with a thick foam mattress to ensure a comfortable rest & sleep for you and your family, along with a white LED light strip and storage bag for convenient nighttime lighting and storage. The ABS hard shell is tough and resistant to breaking, effectively withstanding impacts. Stainless steel support poles smoothly set up the rooftop tent, making it easy to deploy. Recommended for installation on large vehicles such as Jeeps, SUVs, and trucks with roof and crossbar capacities of over 600 lbs. Due to the rooftop tent's weight, multiple people are needed for installation.

- Outdoor & Indoor Use - A stylish addition to the garden, patio, terrace, backyard, balcony, pool, and more, perfect for spending your leisure time alone reading novels on the hammock, or taking it to the beach, camping, picnic for enjoying outdoor views

Product Name: Changing Room, Portable, 2-Room Privacy Tent with Shower Bag & Floor, Blue
Description:
Highlights:
1.- Big Size: The 7.2' x 4.2' size of this portable shower tent allows space to stretch your arms out and move as needed. We all hate hitting our elbows on the wall. The bonus inches cater to the relaxation of getting your time to rinse the dirt off. Despite being sizable, the shower tent packs down into a double-handle bag that's easy to carry.
2.- Double Space: The add-on room on this camp shower tent can be used for changing or a second shower. Getting everybody done faster lets you move on to the next part of the day without dragging on at the prep part.
3.- Shower Bag and Hook: This camping shower tent is ready to use with a 21 L shower bag included. Slip it into the zippered designated area, hang it from a tree branch, or hang it on the hang hook, which could also allow a loofa or a hangable shower catty.
4.- Walls, Windows, and Floor: The walls of this camping bathroom tent are waterproof enough to handle 2,001 mm of water, providing strength. The taffeta fabric is coated to prevent light transmission for privacy, keeping you in your own uninterrupted space. With two mesh windows, air will flow through the waterproof walls. The floor is detachable for letting water out in case it starts to puddle.
5.- Pop Up Bathroom Tent Information: Overall Dimensions: 7.2' L x 4.1' W x 7.5' H. Each Room Size: 3.4' L x 4.1' W x 6.9' H. Assembly Required.

Details:

The 7.2' x 4.1' size of this large shower tent eliminates moments you hit your elbows on the wall. This interior is bigger than some of the cabin showers in camping areas. Product Name: Camping Tent 4 Persons Navy Blue/Yellow
Description:
Details:

This large tent is perfect for all your camping occasions!!

It has a comfortable interior suitable for camping outdoors, travelling and for on vacation at a campsite. This tent is large enough to accommodate up to 4 people.

The tent is easy to build up and it takes only a few minutes to disassemble for storage. The inner wall material is breathable. The floor has a film which is made of PE material.

Delivery also includes a carry bag.

Product Name: 2000W Electric Dual Burner Portable Coil Heating Hot Plate Stove Countertop RV Hotplate with 5 Temperature Adjustments Portable Handles
Description:
Highlights:
1.Equipped with dual 5.5in coil heating elements and 2000W power, it heats up quickly and cooks food evenly
2.5 Temperature levels suit for different demands
3.Independent adjustable thermostat controls and indicator lights for convenient operation.
4.Just simply wipe the non-electrical parts with a damp sponge or half-wet cloth for easy cleaning after cooling down completely and plug removed.
5.Suit for frying pans, woks or stovetop teapots made from aluminum, stainless steel, iron or glass

Details:
*Features*:
*Heating Quickly & Evenly*:Equipped with dual 5.5in coil heating elements and 2000W power,it heats up quickly and cooks food evenly without any hot or cold spots. Use one heating burner to heat tea pot,and other one to prepare soup,working simultaneously and save you much time.
*5 Power Levels*:With 1-5 heating temperature adjustment from 392℉-932℉,easily meet your daily cooking needs,such as boiling water,reheating sauces,making soups,frying steak,cooking pasta,grilling cheese and vegetables,etc.. Independent adjustable thermostat controls and indicator lights for convenient operation.
*Safe Using & Easy Cleaning*:The indicator light on the front of the enclosure will be extinguished when the furnace reaches the temperature you have set. When it is lower than the temperature you set,the light will be on,cycled,and automatically insulated. Just simply wipe the non-electrical parts with a damp sponge or half-wet cloth for easy cleaning after cooling down completely and plug removed.
*Wide Compatibility*:The burner can be used with any flat-bottomed cookware made of a variety of materials,such as frying pans,woks or stovetop teapots made from aluminum,stainless steel,iron or glass. Note:May heat ceramic pot very slowly.
*Compact Design With Handles*:Compact design with portable side handles makes the electric furnace easy to carry,works great in college dorms,small apartments,and RV’s/caravans. Perfect for adventure-seekers,road-trippers,campers and anti-microwave folks. Besides,its body is built with advanced iron with coating for durability.
Warm Tips:
1. When cooking,someone’s better look at it.
2. Do not touch the surface of the heating coil during heating and after heating.
3. Do not immerse the hot plate into the water or other liquids.
4. The hot plate is to heat food,when cooking food the container should be on the heating plate.
5. When the hot plate is not in use,be sure to adjust the switch to the 'off' position and unplug the plug.
6. When using the hot plate for the first time,it should be adjusted to the third level for 3-5 minutes to evaporate the protective film of the furnace surface. At this time,there may be a small amount of smoke emitted,which is normal. It won't happen when use next time.
7. The utensils placed on the hot plate must have a smooth bottom and a diameter that matches the size of the hot plate.
8. If the size of the cooking vessel chassis is smaller than the size of the electric heating plate,it will affect the normal heating area of the heating plate.
9. If the bottom of the vessel is not flat,it can’t be used with the concave and convex situation.
10. When using,do not place other sundries within 30cm/11.81in around the hot plate to prevent blockage and ventilation.

Description:
Highlights:
1.Foldable & Portable: This over fire camp grill boasts a foldable design and comes with a storage bag that is both wearable and beautiful to carry and protect the grill, making it easy to transport anywhere. It can be folded into 18"x12"x1.2" in 5 seconds, which is 6 lbs weight only.
2.High-Quality Steel: The open fire grill is made of heavy-duty steel with a coat of paint on the surface, which is durable, food-grade, rust-proof, and high-temperature heat resistant. It can stand temperatures up to 572Fahrenheit / 300Celsius without deformation and cracking. Load Capacity: 13 lbs / 6 kg.
3.Sturdy & Stable: Unlike other thin legs, our over fire camp grill is durable and stable with thickened legs. It can accommodate multiple pots and pans, ensuring firmness while cooking and grilling.
4.Diamond-Shaped Mesh: The folding campfire grill is designed with a high-density mesh grill, which can transfer heat efficiently and distributes heat evenly. You won't worry about dropping food if you want to cook bacon, eggs, toast, steaks, pancakes, sausages, or even pineapple slices.
5.Multi-Purpose Use: Designed for outdoor cookware, frying pans, skillets, and pots, for cooking over an open fire. Widely used outdoors such as camping, hiking, picnic, traveling, backpacking, climbing, fishing, and other outdoor activities.

Product Name: Instant 2 Second Pop Up;  Portable Outdoor Camping Tent;  Waterproof;  Windproof;  2 Person
Description:
Highlights:
1.Our team of designers and engineers have developed our product, Instant 2 Second Pop Up, Portable Outdoor Camping Tent, Waterproof, Windproof, 2 Person.
2.2 Second Pop up tent! Loosen the yellow strap, Unbuckle all 4 Tent buckles and the tent is ready to be pitched into the ground, that's if there's a lot of wind! For dismantling and packing reverse the steps!
3.Sleeping area dimensions are 47.2" X 82.7 and can fit up to one mattress measuring at 23.6"!
4.Our tent is Waterproof and Wind resistance up to 30 mph! Ventilation's and open areas to keep you cool in warm weathers.
5.With our 2 Second Pop up tent, you will now have more time exploring the wilderness than assembling your tent!

Details:


Product details
Calling all camping enthusiasts and people who are planning their next or first camping adventure. Have you ever tried to assemble a tent and the assembly instructions are not clear at all. Finding yourself hours in with no progress at all. Our team of designers and engineers have developed our product; Instant 2 Second Pop Up; Portable Outdoor Camping Tent; Waterproof; Windproof; 2 Person. Yes! 2 Second Pop up tent! Loosen the yellow strap; Unbuckle all 4 Tent buckles and the tent is ready to be pitched into the ground; that's if there's a lot of wind! For dismantling and packing reverse the steps! Sleeping area dimensions are 47.2" X 82.7 and can fit up to one mattress measuring at 23.6"! Our tent is Waterproof and Wind resistance up to 30 mph! Ventilation's and open areas to keep you cool in warm weathers. With our 2 Second Pop up tent; you will now have more time exploring the wilderness than assembling your tent!

Instant 2 Second Pop Up; Portable Outdoor Camping Tent; Waterproof; Windproof; 2 Person

Easy assembly/dismantling
The product contains: 1 pre-assembled bedroom; 1 waterproof fly sheet; 9 tent pegs; 7 guy ropes; 1 cover.
Instant 2 Second pitching pop up assembly. Guided folding system.
Free standing tent. If there is no major wind; there is no need for pegs. Meaning once you pop open the tent; it is ready to go!

Capacity/Dimensions
Max occupancy: 2 people.
Total Tent weight: 6.4lb. 23.2L
Sleeping area dimensions: 47.2" X 82.7.
The sleeping area has enough space for a self-inflating or backpacking mattress measuring 23.6" maximum. We do not recommend the use of inflating mattresses over 2.4" height in this tent due to the reduction in living space and resistance to condensation.
Size of Transportation cover: 25.6 x 2.8"

Heat resistant
Comes equipped with 1 Ventilation on the back side of the tent.
Additional 2 spaces between the flysheet and the ground on each side in the bedroom to allow air to circulate and keep the natural build-up of condensation to a minimum.
The flysheet fabric filters UV rays with a UPF of 30. Always keep in mind a large amount of UV can pass through a simple open door: protect your skin.

Resistance to wind
We test all tents in a wind tunnel on a turntable to expose each side to the wind. A properly pitched tent with all guy ropes fitted around the tent must remain habitable in wind speeds up to 30 mph near the ground (Force 6).

Waterproof
All our tents are validated in a laboratory (whole tent under 200 L/sqm/h for 4 hours); as well as in the field. (2000 mm PU-coated polyester fly sheet; 4.2 oz./sqm polyethylene groundsheet; all seams sealed using thermo-bonded tape).
A breathable polyester bedroom under the fly sheet means you aren't in contact with the condensation that forms naturally on the inside of the fly sheet.

Description:
Highlights:

*Comfortable Rocking Chair*:Our ergonomic armless rocking chair comes with 11.81x23.22x13.38in spacious sitting area,suitable for women and teenagers. Category: Outdoor>>Camping & Hiking>>Sleeping Bags & Camp Bedding>>Sleeping Pads
Product Name: Self Inflating Folding Camping Sleeping Mattress with Carrying Bag
Description:
Highlights:
1.Quick Inflation and Deflation: This sleeping pad is designed with a double-sided valve which makes inflation and deflation a breeze. You just need to fully open the valve for maximum airflow, then turn the valve to the inflation mode and use the air pump sack to adjust firmness. As for deflation, flip the valve to deflation mode, roll the mat towards the open valve to squeeze out air, and then store it in the bag.
2.2-in-1 Storage Bag: It's worth mentioning that the carrying bag combines storage function and air pump sack in one. Thus, there is no need to buy and carry an extra air pump, saving your money and energy. In addition, the carrying bag is equipped with two handles, bringing you much convenience.
3.High-quality and Durable Material: Made of 30D elastic cloth and 75D polyester pongee with inner TPU coating, this camping sleeping mattress is puncture-proof water repellent, and wear-resistant. It can be used on various terrains, such as sand, grass, and even rugged ground.
4.4" Thickness for Ultra Comfort: Measuring 81" x 29" x 4" (L x W x H), this sleeping pad is big enough to accommodate one person of all sizes. Besides, it's filled with 4" thick high-density sponge which offers better spine support for different people who sleep on their sides, backs and stomachs.
5.Suitable for Various Occasions: Thanks to the easy inflation system, ultralight and portable design, it's a perfect choice for outdoor activities, such as camping, hiking, picnic, backpacking, sunbath and more. Meanwhile, this inflatable camping mat is ideal for all seasons because of its excellent warmth and insulation performance.

Details:

Specifications

Overview
-Easy to inflate and deflate with valve in a few minutes
-Sponge padded mat ensures a comfortable sleeping experience
-Waterproof TPU material is suitable for outdoor use
-Breathable surface for effortless cleaning and maintenance
-Extra carry bag facilitates storage of sleeping mat
-Great option for camping, picnic, traveling, fishing, home, etc
-Compact and lightweight design for easy transportation

Product Name: VEVOR Portable Cooler, 26 QT Hard Cooler with Ice Retention, Heavy-Duty Handles and Strap, Lightweight Rigid Material Insulated Portable Cooler, Suitable for Family Picnics and Short Trips
Description:
Highlights:
1.26QT Large Capacity: This portable cooler provides a 26QT capacity, holding up to 38 cans (330ml / 11 oz), and comes with dividers for organized food storage, perfect for short trips, family picnics, and more.
2.Long-Lasting Cooling: With a 0.9" / 23 mm thick insulation layer, it keeps ice for up to 48 hours at temperatures 0Celsius / 32Fahrenheit and up to 8 hours at temperatures >= 20Celsius / 68Fahrenheit (ice will melt to ice water). Tip: For optimal results, avoid direct sunlight and use at least 40% ice relative to total volume.
3.Lightweight Material: Made from lightweight rigid materials, the cooler weighs only 9 lbs / 4.1kg, reducing outdoor carrying strain.
4.Easy to Carry: The cooler features handles on both sides for easy lifting, whether by one person or more, and a shoulder strap for added convenience and less effort in carrying.
5.Multi-Purpose: This portable cooler is versatile, ideal for outdoor activities like picnics, camping, travel, and fishing, keeping food and drinks fresh and cool for extended periods.

Product Name: 2000W Electric Dual Burner Portable Coil Heating Hot Plate Stove Countertop RV Hotplate with 5 Temperature Adjustments Portable Handles
Description:
Highlights:
1.Equipped with dual 5.5in coil heating elements and 2000W power, it heats up quickly and cooks food evenly
2.5 Adjustable temperature levels
3.The indicator light in the front of the enclosure will be extinguished when the furnace reaches the temperature you have set
4.The burner can be used with any flat-bottomed cookware made of a variety of materials
5.Perfect for adventure-seekers, road-trippers, campers and anti-microwave folks

Details:
*Features*:
*Heating Quickly & Evenly*:Equipped with dual 5.5in coil heating elements and 2000W power,it heats up quickly and cooks food evenly without any hot or cold spots. Use one heating burner to heat tea pot,and other one to prepare soup,working simultaneously and save you much time.
*5 Power Levels*:With 1-5 heating temperature adjustment from 392℉-932℉,easily meet your daily cooking needs,such as boiling water,reheating sauces,making soups,frying steak,cooking pasta,grilling cheese and vegetables,etc.. Independent adjustable thermostat controls and indicator lights for convenient operation.
*Safe Using & Easy Cleaning*:The indicator light on the front of the enclosure will be extinguished when the furnace reaches the temperature you have set. When it is lower than the temperature you set,the light will be on,cycled,and automatically insulated. Just simply wipe the non-electrical parts with a damp sponge or half-wet cloth for easy cleaning after cooling down completely and plug removed.
*Wide Compatibility*:The burner can be used with any flat-bottomed cookware made of a variety of materials,such as frying pans,woks or stovetop teapots made from aluminum,stainless steel,iron or glass. Note:May heat ceramic pot very slowly.
*Compact Design With Handles*:Compact design with portable side handles makes the electric furnace easy to carry,works great in college dorms,small apartments,and RV’s/caravans. Perfect for adventure-seekers,road-trippers,campers and anti-microwave folks. Besides,its body is built with advanced iron with coating for durability.
Warm Tips:
1. When cooking,someone’s better look at it.
2. Do not touch the surface of the heating coil during heating and after heating.
3. Do not immerse the hot plate into the water or other liquids.
4. The hot plate is to heat food,when cooking food the container should be on the heating plate.
5. When the hot plate is not in use,be sure to adjust the switch to the 'off' position and unplug the plug.
6. When using the hot plate for the first time,it should be adjusted to the third level for 3-5 minutes to evaporate the protective film of the furnace surface. At this time,there may be a small amount of smoke emitted,which is normal. It won't happen when use next time.
7. The utensils placed on the hot plate must have a smooth bottom and a diameter that matches the size of the hot plate.
8. If the size of the cooking vessel chassis is smaller than the size of the electric heating plate,it will affect the normal heating area of the heating plate.
9. If the bottom of the vessel is not flat,it can’t be used with the concave and convex situation.
10. When using,do not place other sundries within 30cm/11.81in around the hot plate to prevent blockage and ventilation.
*Specifications*:
​ Product Type: Dual Coil Burner
Color Available: White, Black
Material: Iron Case; Copper Cable
Power: 2000W
Rated Frequency: 60HZ
Voltage: 110V US Plug
Single Plate Weight Capacity: 25kg/55lbs
Dual Plate Weight Capacity: 50kg/110lbs
5 Temperature Gears: First Gear: 100-200℃/212-392℉; Second Gear: 200-300℃/392-572℉; Third Gear: 300-400℃/572-752℉; Fourth Gear: 400-450℃/752-842℉; Fifth Gear: 450-500℃/842-932℉
Hot Plate Diameter: 14cm/5.5in
Power Cable Length: 1m/3.28ft
Item Size: 54x26x8.5cm/21.26x10.24x3.35in
Item Weight: 1715g/3.78lbs
Package Size: 55x28x10cm/21.65x11.02x3.93in
Package Weight: 2100g/4.63lbs
*Package Lists*:
1 x Dual Coil Burner with US Plug
1 x User Manual

*Safe Using & Easy Cleaning*:The indicator light on the front of the enclosure will be extinguished when the furnace reaches the temperature you have set. When it is lower than the temperature you set,the light will be on,cycled,and automatically insulated. Just simply wipe the non-electrical parts with a damp sponge or half-wet cloth for easy cleaning after cooling down completely and plug removed.
*Wide Compatibility*:The burner can be used with any flat-bottomed cookware made of a variety of materials,such as frying pans,woks or stovetop teapots made from aluminum,stainless steel,iron or glass. Note:May heat ceramic pot very slowly.
*Compact Design With Handles*:Compact design with portable side handles makes the electric furnace easy to carry,works great in college dorms,small apartments,and RV’s/caravans. Perfect for adventure-seekers,road-trippers,campers and anti-microwave folks. Besides,its body is built with advanced iron with coating for durability.
Warm Tips:
1. When cooking,someone’s better look at it.
2. Do not touch the surface of the heating coil during heating and after heating.
3. Do not immerse the hot plate into the water or other liquids.
4. The hot plate is to heat food,when cooking food the container should be on the heating plate.
5. When the hot plate is not in use,be sure to adjust the switch to the 'off' position and unplug the plug.
6. When using the hot plate for the first time,it should be adjusted to the third level for 3-5 minutes to evaporate the protective film of the furnace surface. At this time,there may be a small amount of smoke emitted,which is normal. It won't happen when use next time.
7. The utensils placed on the hot plate must have a smooth bottom and a diameter that matches the size of the hot plate.
8. If the size of the cooking vessel chassis is smaller than the size of the electric heating plate,it will affect the normal heating area of the heating plate.
9. If the bottom of the vessel is not flat,it can’t be used with the concave and convex situation.
10. When using,do not place other sundries within 30cm/11.81in around the hot plate to prevent blockage and ventilation.

Product Name: CoolerPak 10lb Ice Pack - Refillable Reusable  Cold for Days  Non-Toxic, Leakproof, Potable Drinking Water Safe  Built Tough, Rolls Up for Storage
Description:
Details:

The patent-pending ice pack solution for keeping your cooler contents cold and dry. CoolerPak is refillable, reusable and space-saving. When not in use, drain and pack it away. CoolerPak is universally designed to work with all coolers. Ditch messy ice and bulky packs for an efficient, eco-friendly cooling upgrade. Enjoy fresh food and beverages on all your adventures with CoolerPak.
Each CoolerPak includes a bonus Snap Screw Kit. To install, simply attach the included paper template to the cooler wall and use a hand screwdriver to secure the screws at the marked mounting points. However, if you prefer not to use the snap screws, the CoolerPak snap to each other and can form their own freestanding walls.

Universally compatible, CoolerPak works seamlessly with any cooler that accommodates its size, ensuring a perfect fit and optimal performance.
The ice that melts inside CoolerPak is potable water and is safe to drink! Please note that the water added before freezing needs to be potable water. Instead of needing to pack both ice and water for your cooler, those that are tight on space can consider the Coolerpak as an alternative water option.
Crafted from 600D TPU flexible fabric, CoolerPak is built to withstand rugged outdoor adventures while maintaining its cooling capabilities.
We put CoolerPak to the test with a 10lb CoolerPak in a 30qt cooler. Impressively, CoolerPak kept the cooler cold for a full 5 days before the temperature rose above 40 degrees. This performance showcases CoolerPak's exceptional cooling capabilities, making it an ideal choice for extended outdoor adventures..table_component { overflow: auto; width: 100%;}.table_component table { border: 1px solid #40bbe9; height: 100%; width: 75%; table-layout: auto; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 1px; text-align: left;}.table_component caption { caption-side: top; text-align: left;}.table_component th { border: 1px solid #40bbe9; background-color: #40bbe9; color: #282e30; padding: 5px;}.table_component td { border: 1px solid #40bbe9; background-color: #bee1ee; color: #282e30; padding: 5px;}

Details:

The patent-pending ice pack solution for keeping your cooler contents cold and dry. CoolerPak is refillable, reusable and space-saving. When not in use, drain and pack it away. CoolerPak is universally designed to work with all coolers. Ditch messy ice and bulky packs for an efficient, eco-friendly cooling upgrade. Enjoy fresh food and beverages on all your adventures with CoolerPak.

Each CoolerPak includes a bonus Snap Screw Kit. To install, simply attach the included paper template to the cooler wall and use a hand screwdriver to secure the screws at the marked mounting points. However, if you prefer not to use the snap screws, the CoolerPak snap to each other and can form their own freestanding walls.

Universally compatible, CoolerPak works seamlessly with any cooler that accommodates its size, ensuring a perfect fit and optimal performance.

The ice that melts inside CoolerPak is potable water and is safe to drink! Please note that the water added before freezing needs to be potable water. Instead of needing to pack both ice and water for your cooler, those that are tight on space can consider the Coolerpak as an alternative water option.

Crafted from 600D TPU flexible fabric, CoolerPak is built to withstand rugged outdoor adventures while maintaining its cooling capabilities.

We put CoolerPak to the test with a 10lb CoolerPak in a 30qt cooler. Impressively, CoolerPak kept the cooler cold for a full 5 days before the temperature rose above 40 degrees. This performance showcases CoolerPak's exceptional cooling capabilities, making it an ideal choice for extended outdoor adventures.

Highlights:
1.This 100 sq ft. tent comfortably fits 2 queen air beds or up to 6 sleeping bags, so you can have your family or group of friends under one roof.
2.The 6-Person Connect Ent easily sets up in about 10 minutes by clipping into your 10 ft. x 10 ft. straight-leg canopy (SOLD SEPARATELY) to convert it to a roomy sleeping area.

Product Name: Outsunny Smokeless Fire Pit with Fireproof Mat, 20" Barrel Style Portable Wood Burning Firepit, Magnesium Oxide Low Smoke Camping Bonfire Stove for Backyard, Patio, Picnic, Brown
Description:
Details:

Product Features:
Smokeless Fire Pit: Keep comfortable when you camp when you finally say goodbye to smoke in your eyes. Our wood-burning, smokeless fire pit lets you enjoy warmth and ambiance without any discomfort.
Secondary Combustion: This smokeless camping fire pit uses a "secondary combustion" process. Bottom vents feed your fire fresh oxygen from below
this oxygen is heated as it rises up the walls, causing conditions that allow smoke to burn away, resulting in clean, smokeless fire.
Designed for Outdoors: Composed of a barrel-like outer shell made of magnesium oxide and a stainless steel combustor, our wood-burning smokeless fire pit isn't just built to endure outdoor conditions
it's an outdoor centerpiece.
Fireproof Mat: For increased safety, our smokeless wood-burning fire pit includes an Aluminum mat to insulate it on the ground and avoid accidents.
Smokeless Deck Fire Pit Info: Overall Dimension: 20.5" Dia. x 15.25" H. Inner Wood Burning Space: 13.25" Dia. Mat Dimension: 22 Dia.

Description:
Highlights:
1.Rapid Pizza Making: A great pizza-making experience is accessible with the pizza oven's ability to reach the perfect temperature in 5-10 minutes and cook pizzas in 2 minutes. Moreover, the cordierite pizza stone can retain and lock in heat, while pizzas cooked over charcoal have a more distinct flavor.
2.Effortless Heat Monitoring: The wood burning pizza oven enables you to monitor the temperature with its built-in thermometer. Thanks to the adjustable design, you can freely adjust the firepower and smoke to gratify your different needs for cooking.
3.Hassle-free Movement: Designed with convenience in mind, the portable pizza maker comes equipped with 4 universal wheels, 2 with brakes and 2 without brakes, allowing for easy relocation. As a result, you are able to move this pizza oven to any desired place.
4.Better Outdoor Adaption: The outdoor pizza maker is constructed with sturdy and rustproof metal tubes for durability and sturdiness. Protected by a high-quality 600D oxford fabric cover that braves any weather, this wood fired pizza oven accompanies you outdoors year-round.

-Cook pizzas quickly with the 750 ℉ max. temperature

-600D Oxford fabric cover adapts to outdoor use
-Open or close the chimney and open or close the burning area for different needs
-Cordierite pizza stone assists in maintaining and trapping heat
-Convenient door handles and removable ash tray ensure easy use

-Please refer to the instruction for specific temperature guidance
-Ideal addition to barbecues, parties, camping and other outdoor activities

Product Name: 12PC 12inch High-strength U-shaped threaded steel ground spikes for multi-purpose pipe and tent anchoring. Durable and windproof.
Description:
Highlights:
1.High-strength threaded steel material: Durable threaded steel offers strong tensile strength, adapts to various soil conditions, and ensures long-term stability.
2.U-shaped design: The U-shaped design effectively distributes pressure, ensuring a secure hold and resisting tilting or shifting.
3.Multi-purpose applications: Suitable for pipe anchoring, tent setting, gardening support, tarpaulin securing, and more, it offers comprehensive functionality to meet a variety of outdoor needs.
4.Wind and Water Resistant: Whether it's strong winds or heavy rain, the U-shaped ground spikes provide strong anchorage, ensuring tents, pipes, and other items remain secure in inclement weather.
5.Easy Installation: The U-shaped design makes it easy to insert into the soil, eliminating the need for complex tools, saving time and effort and ensuring quick installation.

Details:

This U-shaped threaded steel ground spike is made of high-strength threaded steel, featuring a simple design and powerful functionality, suitable for a variety of outdoor anchoring needs. Whether supporting pipes, setting up tents, or securing other temporary structures, the U-shaped ground spike firmly grips the soil, effectively resisting wind and external impact, ensuring a rock-solid stability. The threaded design increases friction with the soil, preventing movement or collapse, making it ideal for camping, gardening, construction, and other applications.

Product Name: Camping Tent 6 Persons Blue and Green
Description:
Details:

This large tent is perfect for all your camping occasions!

It has a comfortable interior suitable for camping outdoors, travelling and for vacation at a campsite. This tent is large enough to accommodate up to 6 people. It features 2 different compartments, each of which offering ample space to accommodate 3 people at maximum. The tent is easy to build up and it takes only a few minutes to disassemble for storage. There are 2 rods included to create an awning of the entrance. The inner wall material is breathable. The floor has a film which is made of PE material. To get a 100% watertight tent, we advise to spray the tent with a water-proof spray. It also has a mosquito net in the sleeping cabin for your summer nights. The included carrying bag is for easy transport.

Good to know: The tent is designed for infrequent and short-term use (performance level 1). Although rain-proof, the tent should be used mainly in fair weather.

Product Name: 3300W Portable Camping Stove Butane Canister Dual Fuel Burner Piezo Electric Ignition Single Burner with Automatic Tank Ejection Overpressure Cut Off Carry Case
Description:
Highlights:
1.Adopt piezo electric ignition, this butane countertop stove is easy to ignite and easy to adjust the heat output
2.It only takes 3-4 minutes to boil 1L water in maximum output
3.Dual fuels design
4.Reliable for camping, outdoor cooking, home emergency kit, etc..
5.It is compact and packs into a plastic case.

Details:
*Features*:
*Piezo Electric Ignition*:Adopt piezo electric ignition,this butane countertop stove is easy to ignite and easy to adjust the heat output. No need for a lighter as the burner ignites automatically,which means no more fumbling with matches!
*8000BTU Portable Stove*:Come with 8 fire outlets,symmetrical and uniform heat,this butane stove is powerful enough to cook anything that you may need on a camping or backpacking trip. It only takes 3-4 minutes to boil 1L water in maximum output.
*Dual Fuels Design*:The camp stove is suitable for standard butane cylinders which are 220ML-250ML. Come with an connection adapter,our portable gas stove can also be connected with propane gas tank.
*Safety Assured*:When the pressure value of the camping stove exceeds the safety factor(5-7kgf/cm²) due to overheating,the tank will automatically fall off,the flow of gas will be cut off and the fire will go out. Reliable for camping,outdoor cooking,home emergency kit,etc..
*Storage Case & Portable*:Dual fuel compatible camp stove is the perfect accessory for camping,hiking,trucking,and other adventures!It is compact and packs into a plastic case.
Friendly Reminder:
1.Stove only,not include canister or gas.
2.Please do not use stone,casseroles cookware in case of gas tank overheating or explosion.
3.Please don’t use sinner benzene,wax to wash,in order to avoid damages such as color changes or paint falls off,and thus caused rust or corrosion
4.When change the gas,please open the windows or ventilator,in order to avoid headache or carbon monoxide poisoning.
5.When use the plug valve(ignition flame-out fire regulation),please don't put hand on the installed cooker and tableware,in order to avoid scalding.
*Specifications*:
​ Product Type: Portable Butane Stove
Materials: Iron, Aluminum Alloy, Plastic
Ignition: Piezo-Electric
Power: 3300W

Dual Fuel Type Support: Butane Fuel(Not Included), Propane Fuel (Liquefied Gas Not Included)
Comptible Fuel Canisters: 220ML-250ML(Most Popular Capacity)

Applicable: 3-5 People

Description:
Highlights:
1.3-in-1 Cooler Table: With an easy-to-lift tabletop, this cooler bar table can perfectly function as a side table, a cocktail table or an ice cooler. And you just need to press the locking button to put down the lid.
2.Weatherproof PP Material: The whole ice cooler is made of premium PP which is sunproof, waterproof and anti-fading. Therefore, the cooler table can withstand long-time outdoor use and bring you prolonged relaxation.
3.Perfect Cooling Solution: The cooler with thickened 3-layer shell and leak-proof design boasts satisfying cooling effect, which can keep cold for 6 hours. Moreover, the 4-gallon capacity of the bucket can accommodate up to 15 cans.
4.Portable Design: Equipped with a convenient handle, this well-made cooler bar table with 6.5 lbs light weight is effortless for you to carry it anywhere. And the bottle opener on one side brings you more convenience.
5.Ideal Outdoor Companion: The cocktail table also comes with a food tong and detachable storage rack for edible ice and lemon slices. And it will be a nice addition to your picnic, camping or just relaxation in the backyard.

Specifications

-Perfect as an ice cooler, cocktail table or a side table
-Weatherproof PP material ensures long-time use
-Thick shell maintains coolness for 12 hours
-Ample 4-gallon capacity holds up to 15 cans
-Portable design with convenient carrying handle
-Integrated bottle opener adds extra convenience
-Includes detachable storage rack and tong
-Ideal for camping, picnic, backyard and so on

Product Name: Camping Tent 6 Persons Blue and Yellow
Description:
Details:

This large tent is perfect for all your camping occasions!

It has a comfortable interior suitable for camping outdoors, travelling and for vacation at a campsite. This tent is large enough to accommodate up to 6 people. It features 2 different compartments, each of which offering ample space to accommodate 3 people at maximum. The tent is easy to build up and it takes only a few minutes to disassemble for storage. There are 2 rods included to create an awning of the entrance. The inner wall material is breathable. The floor has a film which is made of PE material. To get a 100% watertight tent, we advise to spray the tent with a water-proof spray. It also has a mosquito net in the sleeping cabin for your summer nights. The included carrying bag is for easy transport.

Good to know: The tent is designed for infrequent and short-term use (performance level 1). Although rain-proof, the tent should be used mainly in fair weather.

Product Name: Foldable Charcoal BBQ Grill with Shelf Stainless Steel Grill Net Easy Setup Portable Tabletop Barbecue Grill for Camping Picnic Outdoor Party Backyard
Description:
Highlights:
1.Convenient for carrying and transporting
2.Heat-resistant painted iron material
3.Total of 8 heat regulating air vents on the tray allow full air ventilation, making the charcoal burning more quickly.
4.Get together with family and friends and enjoy the outdoor smoky cooking fun and taste the BBQ
5.Easy to set up the grill

Details:
*Features*:
*Portable & Foldable Grill*:With the folding flat piece size of 23.03x8.85x2.55in,this 4.08lbs lightweight and portable charcoal BBQ grill is convenient for carrying and transporting. Ideal for both on the go as well as for patio or backyard cooking.
*Durable Iron Plated Material*:Constructed of high heat-resistant painted iron material,it is corrosion-resistant,and not easy to deform. The grill net is made of food-graded rustproof stainless steel,will not produce hazardous gas when being heated,safe to use.
*Charcoal Drawer Tray*:Equipped with separated charcoal drawer tray,you can easily pull out the drawer to add more charcoals during grilling,without interrupting the production of making delicious food. Product Name: 360 Degree Silent Swivel Hunting Chair
Description:
Highlights:
1.360 Zero Noise Swiveling: Specifically designed with a 360 swiveling base, the folding blind chair will provide all-round vision for an immersive hunting experience. Besides, adopting advanced silent technology, the prey will not be disturbed, thus ensuring a foolproof shot.
2.All-terrain Sink-proof Feet: Equipped with 180-degree swivel duck feet, the adjustable hunting chair will perfectly adapt to uneven grounds and not easy to sink. And the 3.5" feet have a large contact area with the ground to increase friction, thus maintaining stability on gravel roads, muddy grassland and sand.
3.Ergonomic and Comfy Design: The hunting blind chair comes with an ergonomic backrest and adjustable padded armrests to let you hunt in the most comfortable condition. Additionally, the backrest and seat is made of breathable fabric to suit bring you a cool and comfortable experience.
4.Adjustable and Stable Aluminum Legs: The swivel hunting chair is supported by 4 aluminum legs, which is characterized by excellent rust-resistance to ensure long service life. Moreover, the legs feature 3-level height positions to suit different people's diverse needs.
5.Easy to Fold and Transport: The hunting chair can be quickly folded in just three steps, then you can conveniently store it in the corner or carry it to fishing or hunting with the carry strap. Firstly, you need to press the spring button to detach the seat, then fold the legs, and finally fix the legs with bungee cords.

If you are looking for a portable and powerful stoves for your camping, hiking, backpacking, mountaineering, fishing, and picnics, etc.. Portable Stove: Features an included carry bag and 2 handles, our folding camping stove can be easily stored and carried, making your outdoor cooking enjoyable.

So whether you're having a picnic, party or gathering with your family, the beach canopy tent is a perfect choice to enhance your experience.
● Carry and Store with Ease:Featuring a push-button mechanism, the portable beach shelter is set to setup wherever your adventures take you. Weighing only 9.5 lbs, the lightweight tent is easy to transport. And the included carrying bag allows you to conveniently store the beach cabana.

Product Name: 190 Deluxe Portable Liquid Propane, (LP), Gas Grill
Description:
Highlights:
1.190 sq in total cooking surface porcelain-coated grilling grate
2.Convenient, push-button ignition
3.High-temperature finish
4.Lid and firebox
5.Folding legs

Details:

Designed for portable grilling on-the-go, the Gas Grill 190 Deluxe is the perfect solution for your grilling needs. Its compact size and foldable legs make it easily transportable, while the heat-resistant handles allow you to move the grill without waiting for it to cool down. With 190 square inches of cooking surface on a rust-resistant and easy-to-clean porcelain-coated grate, you'll have plenty of space to cook your favorite foods. The convective cooking system is versatile and convenient, powered by portable 16.4 oz disposable propane cylinders (sold separately). Whether you're camping or tailgating, these cylinders are easy to transport. The grill features push-button piezo ignition, eliminating the need for batteries or matches to light it up. Constructed with quality steel and a durable, high-temperature finish, this grill is built to last, resisting rust and extending its lifespan.

Dear Camping Enthusiasts:
 
Are you looking for a camping tent that can perfectly accommodate your family?
 
Do you want to have a good night's sleep with your family after a tiring day of hiking?
 
If so, we are lucky to meet you, our product will be just the one you are looking for!
 
⛺[Spacious & Comfortable for 6 People Family] -- Camping tent with wide design offers enough room for 6 person to sleep comfortably, the external dimension of it is (47.2+84.6+47.2)*84.6*70.9inches, 1 queen air mattresses or 6 sleeping bags are well fit in the tent, suitable for a family to go out camping and play.
 
⛺[Durable & Waterproof Tent] -- Made of premium 210T polyester PU 3000mm fabric, stays completely dry under the light rain, strong and stable, anti-tear, multiple guy lines make the camping tent more windproof, keeps you warm and take you to sweet dreams at night, making your camping trip more enjoyable and comfortable!
 
⛺[Easy to Set Up & Carry] -- No particular skills are needed. Two persons can set it up in 10 minutes. Even for first-time users, installation or disassembly is very convenient and simple. Bigger carry bag size at 27.6x9.1x9.1 inches will let you feel relaxed and easy to repack the tent, weighs 15.2 pounds, which makes you feel no burden and easy to carry the tent to the trunk of car.
 
⛺[Ventilation & Anti-Insect] -- The camping tent has 1 large mesh door and 3 mesh windows, which improves privacy. the gauze design can block mosquitoes, also has anti-UV function, provide a good night's sleep, ideal family tent suitable for car camping or all-weather outdoor travel.
 
⛺[Applicable scene] -- Suit for mountain climbing, angling, fishing, field survival,expedition,picnic, couples & family camping, for all seasons, provide you the comfort of home in the wild of inclement weather.
 
Feature:
 
The lightweight tent can be store in the carry bag, which makes transport easy.
 
Unique fabrics, reinforced sealed seams, 110G PE floor and taped rainfly, rain-proof offer tents a long-lasting life time.
 
Thanks to the waterproof fabric, better prevent rain from dropping inside, top rain fly cover and the seams will not allow rainwater to penetrate.
 
The excellent ground nails and cables make the tent structure more stable, making it easier to build the tent, and the tent will not easily slide on the ground.
 
Ideal for hiking, trekking, traveling, beach camping, backyard camping, or being using as other festival camping tent, perfect in car/ motorcycle/ bicycle trip for family and friends.
 
Sturdy frame, details are designed to provide an excellent camping tent, you can store your mobile phone, wallet and keys and other things in the pocket.
 
An extra large family tent can accommodate 6 people, providing you and your family with the joy of camping and family harmony. allows you to sleep well together under the stars, ideal for 2 parents with 3-4 children.

 1 x Camping Tent, 
 1 x Carry Bag, 
 14 x Nails, 
 4 x guy Lines.

Product Name: Outsunny Smokeless Fire Pit with Fireproof Mat, 20" Barrel Style Portable Wood Burning Firepit, Magnesium Oxide Low Smoke Camping Bonfire Stove for Backyard, Patio, Picnic, Brown
Description:
Details:

Product Features:
Smokeless Fire Pit: Keep comfortable when you camp when you finally say goodbye to smoke in your eyes. Our wood-burning, smokeless fire pit lets you enjoy warmth and ambiance without any discomfort.
Secondary Combustion: This smokeless camping fire pit uses a "secondary combustion" process. Bottom vents feed your fire fresh oxygen from below
this oxygen is heated as it rises up the walls, causing conditions that allow smoke to burn away, resulting in clean, smokeless fire.
Designed for Outdoors: Composed of a barrel-like outer shell made of magnesium oxide and a stainless steel combustor, our wood-burning smokeless fire pit isn't just built to endure outdoor conditions
it's an outdoor centerpiece.
Fireproof Mat: For increased safety, our smokeless wood-burning fire pit includes an Aluminum mat to insulate it on the ground and avoid accidents.
Smokeless Deck Fire Pit Info: Overall Dimension: 20.5" Dia. x 15.25" H. Inner Wood Burning Space: 13.25" Dia. Mat Dimension: 22 Dia.

Product Name: 2-Person Outdoor Camping Tent with External Cover
Description:
Highlights:
1.Suitable for Summer and Winter: Thanks to ventilated mesh windows on all sides of the tent, you can enjoy the breeze when relaxing in the tent during fuggy afternoon. Besides, there is an extra external cover to create a double protection for warmth. So you can sleep in a cozy place outdoors without enduring the chilliness.
2.Self-Inflating Sleeping Mat: Unscrew the gas nozzle counterclockwise, this air-filled mattress will be automatically inflated in 5-8 minutes, saving your time and energy. And the mat is designed with pillow, no need on taking much beddings, providing comfortable sleeping experience.
3.Elevated Cot with Sturdy Frame: This 2-person cot with heavy-duty metal frame offers excellent durability and sturdiness, which can load up to 660 lbs. And the elevated cot offers a safe place without worrying about muddy water encroachment and insect problems in outdoor activities. Extra fixation straps and metal stakes enhance wind resistance and stability.
4.Large Roller Carrying Bag: Comes with a large carrying bag, all accessories can be packed in it, also you can put it in the trunk for easy transportation and store in the corner when not in use. Since the extra rollers and handles, you can carry the bag effortlessly. Besides, the roller bag can load up to 55lbs.
5.Meet All Your Daily Needs: This camping cot tent set can be used in combination and separately. When you used it alone, the bottom moisture proof segregation fabric of this large tent will protect you from damp ground and offer a comfortable dry place. Besides, the inside hanging hook is specially designed for lamp placing, and bottom shoe pocket ensures convenient storage.

Details:

Specifications
Overview
This functional camping combo consists of a camping cot below and a tent above, keeping you off the ground and avoiding humidity inside.

Extra pillow and sleeping bed are attached for better comfort. Besides, the bed is automatically inflated by simply opening the gas nozzle. Our tent adopts a double-layer design with a ventilated inner and waterproof outer layer. And you can take down the outer tent according to your specific needs. The unique double windows, namely oxford and mesh, not only ventilate the interior, but also keep warm. Wide doors with zippers offer free access and smooth close. The tent is big enough for 2 adults. With the side pocket for your phones and shoe storage bag, this tent creates much convenience for you. If you need a bright space at night, then the hook is for you to hang on a lamp. The cross-shaped iron pipes provide strong support, loading up to 660lbs. The tent is light and portable, and there is a storage bag with wheels for you to take outdoors.

If you are looking for a outdoor tent like this, do not hesitate to place an order!

Product Name: Rooftop Tent Hard Shell with USB Outlet, Winter Thermal Liner, Summer Side Awning&Luggage Racks for 4 Season Camping, Aluminum Pop Up 2-3 Person Roof Top Tent for Truck Jeep SUV Van Trailer
Description:
Highlights:
1.Pioneer HD rooftop tent comes with multi-port USB outlet, winter detachable thermal liner, summer attachable side awning and adjustable luggage racks.
2.Made from durable 320g polyester, aircraft-grade aluminum hardshell with aluminium round corners, hydraulic gas struts, waterproof rubber seal and flocked lining tent floor to prevent moisture.
3.Include a 3-layer built-in detachable mattress, YKK zipper netting windows, interior storage pouches, a built-in LED light strip, 7.68' extendable aluminum ladder and 2 detachable shoe storage bags.
4.Fit up to 2-3 adults with its spacious square design and pop up easily in just 5 seconds.
5.Compatible with nearly any vehicle equipped with proper cross bars. Requires cross bars with a dynamic weight load of at least 195 lbs.

Details:
Upgrades Tailored for You
1 - Built-in USB Outlet: Enhance comfort for work and entertainment.
2 - Winter Detachable Thermal Liner: Offer extra warmth and comfort during cold weather.
3 - Summer Attachable Side Awning: Offer additional shade and protection from sun and rain for outdoor enjoyment.
4 - Adjustable Luggage Racks: Provide convenient storage for extra luggage and personal items.
5 - Aircraft-grade Aluminum Hardshell: Provide superior durability and protection.
Features Designed for You
6 - 320g Polyester with YKK Zipper Netting Windows and Windproof Layers: Enhanced protection against the elements.
7 - 3-Layer Luxurious Mattress: Upgraded with a flocked lining tent floor to prevent condensation.
A. 1.96" (5 cm) Thick Non-Deformable Sleeping Mat: Made of high-quality, high-density foam that contours to your body for excellent support, promoting restful sleep all night after a day of adventure—just like at home.
B. 0.39" (1.0 cm) Condensation Mat: Acts as a barrier, addressing the common issue of moisture build-up in outdoor life and preventing condensation from reaching the sleeping surface.
C. 0.20" (0.5 cm) Ocean Mat: Absorbs moisture effectively, ensuring a dry and comfortable sleeping experience.
D. Flocked Lining Tent Floor: Upgraded with flocked lining compared to other tents, providing dual-layer protection against condensation and moisture buildup.
8 - Additional Details: Includes interior storage pouches, built-in LED light strip, 1 aluminum ladder with ladder storage bag (7.6') and 2 waterproof shoe storage bags (20" x 20").
Specifications
Package Dimensions: 88.00" x 56.00" x 8.54"
Package Weight: 269 lbs
Expanded Size (Opened): 83.86" x 51.57" x 39.57"
Compact Size (Closed): 83.86" x 51.57" x 7.00"
Weight: 199 lbs
Side Awning Size and Weight: 78.74"*78.74"(2*2m), 3.30lbs(1.5kg)
Mattress: 79.50"*48.00"*2.56"(202*122*6.5cm)
Led Light Strip: 59.84"(1.52m)
Telescopic Rods: Extendable Height to 7.55' (2.3m)
Ladder: Extendable Height to 7.68' (2.35m)

HTML Description:
Details:

This family tent with a modern look protects you from the unpleasant weather and provides a comfortable place for anywhere adventures.

 

  • All-round waterproof design: This camping tent, made from polyester with a PU coating, is waterproof and wind proof. The taped seams effectively prevent rainwater infiltration, while the heavy-duty ground sheet helps maintain a dry and comfortable interior.
  • White blackout fabric: The specially designed tent fabric blocks out 99% daylight, ensuring a cooler and more comfortable sleep environment. Say goodbye to early morning sunlight disturbances and enjoy a restful night's sleep.

  • Detachable rainfly: The detachable rainfly can be attached to the tent's top for weather protection and privacy.
  • Good ventilation & mosquito protection: The mesh walls not only offer excellent ventilation but also ensure a comfortable experience for users.
  • Convenient electrical cord access: The E-port allows you to easily connect an extension cord from an external power source to your tent.

Product Name: VEVOR Camping Shower Tent, 2-Room Foldable Portable Privacy Tent Changing Room with Ground Stakes, Ropes, and Carry Bag, 150D Oxford Fabric with Silver Coating, for Camping, Beach, and Fishing
Description:
Highlights:
1.Security & Privacy Protection: When showering or changing outdoors, both matter. The thick outer fabric and fiberglass frame keep the camping shower tent stable in wind or rain, while ventilation and interior storage add home-like convenience
2.Easy to Set Up and Fold: The quick-fold design lets you collapse the shower tent quickly, reducing its size for easy storage without taking up space. Setup is equally simple-no special skills required, and even beginners can assemble it with ease
3.Spacious 2-Room Design: The 84.25 x 44.09 x 83.86 in space allows two people to use the outdoor shower tent at once. Its dual-zone layout supports dry-wet separation, letting you shower in one area while drying off or changing clothes in the other
4.Sun Protection & Water Resistance: Made of 150D Oxford fabric with UPF 50 protection, our privacy tent blocks harsh sunlight. Side windows improve airflow. PU2000mm water resistance lets rain slide off quickly, keeping the interior dry
5.Multiple Storage Options: This portable shower tent provides home-like convenience outdoors. The top hook holds a light or shower head, the storage pocket keeps phones and small items organized, and the tissue bag adds extra convenience

Details:
Comfortable Outdoor Privacy Space Our camping shower tent is made with UPF 50 sun protection and PU2000 mm water-resistant fabric to block sun and rain at the beach or campsite, keeping the interior dry and comfortable. Our outdoor shower tent includes several storage pockets, a clothesline, and hanging hooks, making it easy to store towels, clothing, phones, and other items. These thoughtful features provide a more convenient and comfortable experience. The detachable rain fly helps handle light showers with ease, while the detachable floor mat works well on grass and sand and is easy to clean. These flexible designs allow the shower tent to adapt to various outdoor environments. No extra tools are required, so even beginners can complete the setup quickly. With our portable shower tent, you can enjoy instant privacy wherever you go. Our privacy tent is lightweight and portable for camping, beach trips, photography, or fishing. It provides a private space for changing, showering, or resting outdoors.

Product Name: VEVOR Truck Bed Tent, 6.4'-6.7' Pickup Truck Tent with Rain Layer and Carry Bag, Waterproof PU2000mm Double Layer Truck Tent, Accommodate 2-3 Person, for Camping Traveling Outdoor Activities
Description:
Highlights:
1.Compatible with Various Vehicles: Are you ready to get more out of your truck? The VEVOR pickup tent is suitable for pickup trucks with a 6.4-6.7 feet bed and is compatible with Ford F150, Dodge Ram 1500, GMC Sierra, Chevrolet Silverado, Nissan Titan, Toyota Tundra, and more. With this tent, you can turn your truck into a mobile "home" and enjoy outdoor camping fun with your family and friends.
2.Stand up to Rain: The VEVOR pickup tent has a waterproof rating of up to PU2000. It has a double-layer tent with a rainfly that effectively prevents fierce wind and heavy rainfall. Additionally, it has a 120g fully sewn PE floor with a waterproof pressing process, which prevents the tent's interior from soaking, even during heavy rain.
3.Safer and Sturdier: The VEVOR pickup tent has a streamlined design that reduces wind resistance. It also has thickened 9mm fiberglass support poles that are corrosion-resistant and provide solid support. The sturdy tent can withstand force 5 wind, ensuring your safety even in windy weather.
4.Room for the Family: The pickup tent has a maximum height of 5.58 feet in the middle, providing a roomy space for a family to rest. It also has high-density mesh windows that prevent bugs from entering during the summer. The small window in the outer tent enhances airflow, ensuring a more refreshing resting experience.
5.Take on Any Challenge: The truck bed tent is breathable and bug-proof, enabling you to enjoy the sky and maintain a clear view through the skylight. You can pull the rainfly outside the tent while you sleep. The double-layer design makes the tent resistant to cold and rain, ensuring a peaceful sleep. The dual usage allows you to adapt to the changing outdoor environment.

Details:
VEVOR Truck Bed Tent, 6.4'-6.7' Pickup Truck Tent with Rain Layer and Carry Bag, Waterproof PU2000mm Double Layer Truck Tent, Accommodate 2-3 Person, for Camping Traveling Outdoor Activities

Specifications

-The out cover is machine washable for your convenience

-Roll the mattress up and fixed by the straps and buckles for easy storage

Description:

● Various Fuel Options and Accessories:You can choose wood pellets, firewood, lump charcoal, or wood chips to keep a continuous flame. The 4-in-1 pizza oven can be assembled and installed quickly to be an ideal oven for indoor or outdoor BBQ grilling, gathering parties, or camping trips to enjoy a happy time with your family and friends.

Product Name: VEVOR Camping Shower Tent, 83" x 42" x 83" 2 Rooms Oversize Outdoor Portable Shelter, Privacy Tent with Detachable Top, Pockets, Hanging Rope and Clothesline, for Dressing, Changing, Toilet, Bathroom
Description:
Highlights:
1.Privacy in the Wild: Do you here the call from nature? Amid the call of the great outdoors, your security and privacy are our top concerns. This camping shower tent is made of thickened Oxford fabric and a fiberglass frame to withstand harsh outdoor conditions. Completed with side windows and various storage designs, it provides you with the security and convenience of a home bathroom.
2.Take on Tough Conditions: Our outdoor shower tent is crafted from a combination of 190T polyester and 210D Oxford fabric. It offers UV50 protection to shield you from the scorching sun, while the two windows provide proper ventilation to prevent stuffiness. In addition, the tent has a waterproof rating of PU2000mm, which ensures rainwater slides off quickly without penetrating the tent.
3.Feel Just Like Home: The storage design of our shower tents for camping provides convenience and comfort like a home bathroom. From the clothesline for clothes and towels, ceiling cords for hanging lights and showerheads, to two storage bags and hooks for essentials, it ensures convenience and comfort for temporary outdoor showers and changing.
4.Shower in Comfort: We have made significant improvements to our shower tent, ensuring high quality in every detail. Our smooth SBS zippers allow for easy access, while the storage bag makes packing up a breeze. The button system makes securing the door effortlessly, and the mesh windows provide excellent ventilation. All of these features are designed to offer you a comfortable and private space.
5.Multifunctional Tent: This privacy tent measures 83" x 42" x 83", providing plenty of space for 2 people to move around comfortably during showers. It provides good ventilation when used as a mobile toilet. Additionally, when shooting outdoors, it serves as a temporary dressing room, making it convenient to change clothes and store garments.

Details:
2-Room Outdoor Shower Tent Ready to enjoy the outdoors? Our shower tent is made of extra-thick Oxford fabric, providing unmatched privacy protection. It has a spacious size of 83" x 42" x 83", which allows for 2 people using. Stay clean, refreshed, and ready to continue your adventure with VEVOR! Our shower tent for camping adopts polyester and 210D Oxford fabric, which is waterproof and sun-proof. It ensures non-light penetration for absolute privacy. Thanks to the side windows and top opening, you'll enjoy delightful ventilation even in summer. Our tent stands out from regular shower tents with its user-friendly storage upgrade. It includes side pockets and hooks that make it easy to store small items, and the top cord and clothesline allow for hanging clothing. These features address common challenges encountered during outdoor showering. This portable shower tent showcases excellence in every detail. From the smooth SBS zippers, handy storage bag, and easy-to-use buttons to the mesh windows, each element provides a comfortable and convenient space for you. Whether you're camping outdoors and require a temporary toilet and quick shower space, or you're conducting an outdoor photoshoot needing a dressing room, this privacy tent provides the perfect solution.

Product Name: Outsunny Smokeless Fire Pit with Fireproof Mat, 20" Barrel Style Portable Wood Burning Firepit, Magnesium Oxide Low Smoke Camping Bonfire Stove for Backyard, Patio, Picnic, Black
Description:
Details:

Product Features:
Smokeless Fire Pit: Keep comfortable when you camp when you finally say goodbye to smoke in your eyes. Our wood-burning, smokeless fire pit lets you enjoy warmth and ambiance without any discomfort.
Secondary Combustion: This smokeless camping fire pit uses a "secondary combustion" process. Bottom vents feed your fire fresh oxygen from below
this oxygen is heated as it rises up the walls, causing conditions that allow smoke to burn away, resulting in clean, smokeless fire.
Designed for Outdoors: Composed of a barrel-like outer shell made of magnesium oxide and a stainless steel combustor, our wood-burning smokeless fire pit isn't just built to endure outdoor conditions it's an outdoor centerpiece.
Fireproof Mat: For increased safety, our smokeless wood-burning fire pit includes an Aluminum mat to insulate it on the ground and avoid accidents.
Smokeless Deck Fire Pit Info: Overall Dimension: 20.5" Dia. x 15.25" H. Inner Wood Burning Space: 13.25" Dia. Mat Dimension: 22 Dia.

The camping hammock with mosquito net allows you to experience peaceful relaxation without mosquito bother. It is the ideal hammock for camping, backpacking, hunting, traveling and also great for your backyard, terrace, bedroom.

Forget the tent

Description:
Highlights:
1.Aluminium Hard Shell with Aluminium Round Corner and Stainless Steel Gas Struts: Durable and built to endure the ever-changing season.
2.Side Awning: Offer extra shade and protection from the sun and rain, perfect for enjoying the outdoors.
3.Air Conditioner Outlet with Detachable Bracket: Provide a robust and stable support for elevating and stabilizing your portable air conditioner.
4.Replaceable Rain Flies/Rain Curtains: Allow you to easily replace the rain fly/rain curtain, ensuring flexibility and long-lasting protection.
5.3 Layer Luxurious Mattress, Upgraded with Flocked Lining Tent Floor to Prevent Condensation, with Flocked Lining Tent Floor: Ugraded with flocked lining compared to others's tent, dual-layer protection against condensation and moisture buildup.

Details:

About this item

1. Polyester, Nylon Mesh, Black Vinyl Coating

2. [Upgraded Roof Top Tent to 100% Market Excellence] - HEYFUN rooftop tents are standout options with premium features including extra attachable side awning, air conditioner outlet with detachable bracket, adjustable luggage racks and replaceable rain flies, best travel solution for carrying more luggage and perfect choice for camping enthusiasts and seasoned adventurers of all levels valuing quality and affordability.

3. [Hardshell Rooftop Tent with Top Configuration 3 Layer Luxurious Mattress] - The suv car rooftop tent is designed with thick wear-resistant polyester, honeycomb aluminum hardshell with aluminium round corner, stainless steel gas struts, 3-layer built-in mattress, flocked lining tent floor, 13 interior ceiling&sidewall storage pouches, zipper netting windows and upper small mesh window, providing structural strength&rigidity, UV-resistant, waterproof, breathable and resistant to moisture.

4. [2-3 People Bed Tent for Camping with Spacious Visibility] - The truck bed tent, with closed dimensions of 83.86"*51.57"*7.00" (213*131*17.8cm) and opened dimensions of 83.86"*51.57"*62.99" (213*131*160cm), offers ample space to accommodate two adults and one child with maximum load 660lbs, suitable for camping with your family, loved ones or friends, ensuring a broad perspective to enjoy panoramic views of your surroundings while also maintaining good privacy for camping in the nature.

5. [Pop up Overland Rooftop Tent with 5 Seconds to Open and Close] - The hydraulic automatic top tent, easily pop up or put away with rust-resistant&corrosion-resistant stainless steel gas struts in 5 seconds, can be used continuously for many years without losing stability for Truck Jeep SUV Car Van Wrangler Tacoma Minivan.

6. [4-Season Offroad Roof Tent with Complete Accessories in the Wooden Package] - The rugged all-weather universal outdoor roof top tent for year-round adventures is equipped with pre-assembled components with clear instructions effortless even for first-time users.

7. [HEYFUN Tent Warranty for 2 Years] - 30-day money-back guarantee for product returns. 2-Year limited warranty covering any manufacturer's defects from the date of purchase, excluding damage resulting from misuse. Lifetime accessory replacement support available. Friendly Reminder: Uninstall and remove the air conditioning bracket when packing up the Rooftop Tent and moving to another location. Dry the Rooftop Tent thoroughly before storing it after use on a rainy day.

Product Name: Camping Tent 4 Persons Gray and Orange
Description:
Details:

This large tent is perfect for all your camping occasions! It has a comfortable interior suitable for camping outdoors, travelling and for on vacation at a campsite.

This tent is large enough to accommodate up to 4 people. The tent is easy to build up and it takes only a few minutes to disassemble for storage. The inner wall material is breathable. The floor has a film which is made of PE material. To get a 100% watertight tent, we advise to spray the tent with a water-proof spray. The included carry bag is for easy transport and storage.

Note: This 4-man tent sleeps four persons, but we'd recommend this tent for a pair of campers with their gear so you will have the space and comfort you need.

Good to know: The tent is designed for infrequent and short-term use (performance level 1). Although rain-proof, the tent should be used mainly in fair weather.

Product Name: Outsunny Smokeless Fire Pit with Fireproof Mat, 20" Barrel Style Portable Wood Burning Firepit, Magnesium Oxide Low Smoke Camping Bonfire Stove for Backyard, Patio, Picnic, Black
Description:
Details:

Product Features:
Smokeless Fire Pit: Keep comfortable when you camp when you finally say goodbye to smoke in your eyes. Our wood-burning, smokeless fire pit lets you enjoy warmth and ambiance without any discomfort.
Secondary Combustion: This smokeless camping fire pit uses a "secondary combustion" process. Bottom vents feed your fire fresh oxygen from below
this oxygen is heated as it rises up the walls, causing conditions that allow smoke to burn away, resulting in clean, smokeless fire.
Designed for Outdoors: Composed of a barrel-like outer shell made of magnesium oxide and a stainless steel combustor, our wood-burning smokeless fire pit isn't just built to endure outdoor conditions it's an outdoor centerpiece.
Fireproof Mat: For increased safety, our smokeless wood-burning fire pit includes an Aluminum mat to insulate it on the ground and avoid accidents.

Product Name: Rectangular Heated Sleeping Bag, Lightweight Sleeping Bag with Multi USB Powered Heating Pads, Waterproof Compact Envelope Sleeping Bag for Backpacking Hiking, Gray
Description:
Details:

Introductions:
Stay warm and comfortable during your outdoor adventures with this innovative rectangular heated sleeping bag. Designed for versatility, it features a built-in electronic heating system powered by USB, allowing you to connect it easily to power banks or other USB power sources. The outer shell is crafted from high-quality, durable 190T polyester, making it waterproof and tough enough to withstand years of regular use while remaining soft against the skin. Whether you are camping in the mountains, relaxing at the beach, or needing a quick nap at the office, this bag ensures a restful experience. It includes a smooth zipper secured with velcro and an adjustable drawstring hood to trap heat effectively. Despite its advanced heating capabilities, the bag remains ultralight and portable, offering the perfect balance of warmth and convenience for hiking, backpacking, and RV travel.
Features:
1. Multi-Zone Electronic Heating: Equipped with a 4-piece heating pad 3D system, this sleeping bag targets key areas including the shoulder, chest, hip, and feet. The system is compatible with various USB power supplies such as cellphone chargers, power banks, and car jump starters, providing consistent warmth where you need it most.
2. Adjustable Temperature Control: This heated sleeping bag offers three distinct levels of heating to suit your comfort needs. You can easily adjust the settings to warm your body during chilly nights or lower the temperature mode if you feel too hot, making it suitable for use across all seasons.
3. Durable and Waterproof Material: Constructed with a high-quality 190T polyester shell, this bag is designed to stand up to years of rugged outdoor use. The waterproof exterior protects against moisture and damp conditions, ensuring you stay dry and comfortable whether you are in a tent or sleeping under the stars.
4. Secure Heat Retention Design: Features a smooth zipper secured with a velcro strap and a drawstring hood for precise adjustment. By tugging the drawstrings, you can bring the headrest closer to your body, sealing in warmth and providing extra insulation against cold air during lower temperatures.
5. Ultralight and Versatile Usage: Weighing only 3.3 lbs, this sleeping bag is easy to carry and perfect for backpacking, hiking, and camping. Its versatile design makes it an excellent choice for sleeping at home, in the office, backyard, car, or RV, balancing high performance with lightweight materials.
Specifications:
1. Dimensions: (82.7 x 33.5) in / (210 x 85) cm
2. Weight: 3.3 lbs
3. Temperature Range: 14-50 °F
Package Includes:
1 x Sleeping Bag
