Product Name: VEVOR 3 Person Camping Tent, Waterproof Lightweight Backpacking Tent for Outdoor Family Camping,Hiking,Hunting, Mountaineering Travel 7'x7'x48"
Description:
Highlights:
1.Enjoy Camping Again: The camping tent is spacious, measuring 7 x 7 x 4 ft, and can comfortably accommodate 3 adults with sleeping bags or 2-3 people with plenty of luggage. With reinforced corners, the tent can withstand strong winds and rain, ensuring a secure and enjoyable camping experience for your family.
2.Beat the Rain: Our tent is constructed using PU2000mm waterproof tent fabric, ensuring excellent water resistance. The adhesive-sealed seams effectively prevent seepage, allowing rainwater to glide down effortlessly. Additionally, the 150D Oxford base efficiently filters ground dampness and guards against potential leakage. Bid farewell to concerns about unpredictable weather during your outdoor escapades.
3.Enjoy Your Summer: The camp tent is crafted from anti-UV50 sun-protection fabric, ensuring exceptional resistance to harmful UV rays even under the blazing sun. The fabric's double-seam weaving technique prevents aging and tearing, extending its lifespan. Bid farewell to concerns about the scorching summer sun and the risk of getting tanned.
4.A Breath of Fresh Air: Our backpacking tent features a door to ensure ventilation during summer. The high-density mesh windows keep unwanted insects at bay while ensuring constant fresh air circulation. Close the outer doors and windows to cocoon yourself in privacy without compromising comfort.
5.Unbeatable Camping Experience: This lightweight tent has 0.3" fiberglass pop-up poles, smooth 3F zippers, and convenient inside storage pockets for small items. There's also an E-Port at the bottom for easy access to power. It's perfect for casual camping, backyard lounging, festivals, beach gatherings, and other outdoor events.

Details:
Embrace the thrill of the outdoors like never before! Ready to camp? Our camping tent provides style and comfort. It is ample enough to accommodate up to 3 people. And the reinforced corners ensure structural integrity to withstand strong winds and heavy rain. Your family will enjoy a secure and worry-free overnight camping experience. Tackle any weather with our fully enclosed ground design, providing reliable waterproofing. From sunshine to rain, our tent effortlessly deals with ever-changing weather conditions. Acting as your outdoor sun-protective clothing, our backpacking tent effectively shields you and your family from UV rays while providing significant heat insulation. Our hiking tent with a door and window design ensures free air circulation between the interior and exterior, keeping the environment inside fresh and breathable. Our tents for camping cater to every outdoor desire with an eye for detail. Embrace the richness of nature, and soak in the pure joy of camping in style and comfort.

Product Name: CoolerPak Ice Pack -Refillable Reusable  Cold for Days  Non-Toxic, Leakproof, Potable Drinking Water Safe  Built Tough, Rolls Up for Storage
Description:
Details:

The patent-pending ice pack solution for keeping your cooler contents cold and dry. CoolerPak is refillable, reusable and space-saving. When not in use, drain and pack it away. CoolerPak is universally designed to work with all coolers. Ditch messy ice and bulky packs for an efficient, eco-friendly cooling upgrade. Enjoy fresh food and beverages on all your adventures with CoolerPak.
Each CoolerPak comes with your choice of a snap or hook and loop attachments along with instructions. However, if you prefer not to use these attachments, the CoolerPak snap to each other and can form their own freestanding walls.

Universally compatible, CoolerPak works seamlessly with any cooler that accommodates its size, ensuring a perfect fit and optimal performance.
The ice that melts inside CoolerPak is potable water and is safe to drink! Please note that the water added before freezing needs to be potable water. Instead of needing to pack both ice and water for your cooler, those that are tight on space can consider the Coolerpak as an alternative water option.
Crafted from 600D TPU flexible fabric, CoolerPak is built to withstand rugged outdoor adventures while maintaining its cooling capabilities.

We put CoolerPak to the test with a 10lb CoolerPak in a 30qt cooler. Impressively, CoolerPak kept the cooler cold for a full 5 days before the temperature rose above 40 degrees. This performance showcases CoolerPak's exceptional cooling capabilities, making it an ideal choice for extended outdoor adventures.

Product Name: Rectangular Heated Sleeping Bag, Lightweight Sleeping Bag with Multi USB Powered Heating Pads, Waterproof Compact Envelope Sleeping Bag for Backpacking Hiking, Red
Description:
Details:

Introductions:
Stay warm and comfortable during your outdoor adventures with this innovative rectangular heated sleeping bag. Designed for versatility, it features a built-in electronic heating system powered by USB, allowing you to connect it easily to power banks or other USB power sources. The outer shell is crafted from high-quality, durable 190T polyester, making it waterproof and tough enough to withstand years of regular use while remaining soft against the skin. Whether you are camping in the mountains, relaxing at the beach, or needing a quick nap at the office, this bag ensures a restful experience. It includes a smooth zipper secured with velcro and an adjustable drawstring hood to trap heat effectively. Despite its advanced heating capabilities, the bag remains ultralight and portable, offering the perfect balance of warmth and convenience for hiking, backpacking, and RV travel.
Features:
1. Multi-Zone Electronic Heating: Equipped with a 4-piece heating pad 3D system, this sleeping bag targets key areas including the shoulder, chest, hip, and feet. The system is compatible with various USB power supplies such as cellphone chargers, power banks, and car jump starters, providing consistent warmth where you need it most.
2. Adjustable Temperature Control: This heated sleeping bag offers three distinct levels of heating to suit your comfort needs. You can easily adjust the settings to warm your body during chilly nights or lower the temperature mode if you feel too hot, making it suitable for use across all seasons.
3. Durable and Waterproof Material: Constructed with a high-quality 190T polyester shell, this bag is designed to stand up to years of rugged outdoor use. The waterproof exterior protects against moisture and damp conditions, ensuring you stay dry and comfortable whether you are in a tent or sleeping under the stars.
4. Secure Heat Retention Design: Features a smooth zipper secured with a velcro strap and a drawstring hood for precise adjustment. By tugging the drawstrings, you can bring the headrest closer to your body, sealing in warmth and providing extra insulation against cold air during lower temperatures.
5. Ultralight and Versatile Usage: Weighing only 3.3 lbs, this sleeping bag is easy to carry and perfect for backpacking, hiking, and camping. Its versatile design makes it an excellent choice for sleeping at home, in the office, backyard, car, or RV, balancing high performance with lightweight materials.
Specifications:
1. Dimensions: (82.7 x 33.5) in / (210 x 85) cm
2. Weight: 3.3 lbs
3. Temperature Range: 14-50 °F
Package Includes:
1 x Sleeping Bag

Product Name: (FST-RV-11)Personal Water Filter for Hiking, RV Camping, Travel, and Emergency Preparedness
Description:
Details:
Product Function:Our Personal Water Filter is designed to provide on-the-go access to safe, clean drinking water in a variety of settings. Utilizing advanced filtration technology, it effectively removes bacteria, viruses, protozoa, heavy metals, and other contaminants, ensuring that you have access to pure water no matter where your adventures take you. The compact and portable design allows for easy use directly from natural sources such as rivers, lakes, or streams, giving you peace of mind in any outdoor or emergency scenario.Application Scenarios:
Hiking: Lightweight and compact, this water filter fits perfectly in your backpack, enabling you to hydrate safely during long treks through uncharted territories.RV Camping: Whether you're parked by a serene lake or exploring national parks, our filter ensures that your RV's water supply or freshly fetched water from nearby sources is clean and safe for drinking.Travel: Perfect for international travelers who might encounter uncertain water quality. Easily slip it into your luggage to guarantee clean drinking water wherever your journey leads.Emergency Preparedness: In times of natural disasters or unexpected emergencies, having a reliable water filtration system can be a lifesaver. Our filter allows you to convert any available water source into safe drinking water, supporting your family's hydration needs until help arrives.Product Specifications:
Filtration Capacity: Capable of filtering up to 0.7 liter of water, ensuring long-lasting use before needing replacement filters.Filtration Technology: Utilizes a multi-stage filtration process, including a 0.1-micron absolute filter, to remove 99.9999% of bacteria, 99.99% of viruses, and 99.9% of protozoa, as well as reducing chemicals and heavy metals.Weight & Dimensions: Weighing just under a pound and measuring a compact 8.66 inches in length, it's designed to be highly portable without compromising performance.Ease of Use: One-handed operation with a simple pump mechanism. Includes a durable carrying case and extra filter cartridges for extended trips.Compatibility: Suitable for use with standard water bottles, hydration bladders, and can even be adapted for direct inline use with some hydration systems.Our Personal Water Filter is your ultimate companion for ensuring clean, safe drinking water in any environment, making it an essential addition to your outdoor gear, camping essentials, travel pack, and emergency preparedness kit.

Product Name: USB Heated Blanket Electric Heated Poncho Shawl Wrap Throw with Zipper Arm Holes Pocket 3 Heating Levels 6 Zones Dual Switch 5V/2A Machine Washable for Home Office Outdoor
Description:
Highlights:
1.2 Size options.2 Color options
2.3-level heating modes
3.Work As Blanket and Shawl
4.USB Powered & Machine Washable
5.Super soft polyester lining with short plush

Details:
*Features*:
*6 Heated Zones & Dual-Switch*:This heating blanket has 6 heating panels including 4 back areas and 2 pocket parts. With dual switch to control the back heating areas and pocket areas individually as needed. Just slip the heated shawl on to feel chill-busting warmth surrounding your body that will keep you working or playing outside even longer.
*3 Temperature Levels*:Designed with 3-level heating modes,you can just long press to turn on and short press to switch during 113-122-131℉ to fit your need and customize your comfort on the go. If you start to feel too warm,simply long press to turn it off and enjoy it as a regular piece of outerwear/blanket.
*Work As Blanket & Shawl*:With special zipper design on the blanket,you can wear it as a shawl after zipping out two arm holes. Equipped with several snap buttons,you can customize your own wearing styles. You can also zip in two arm holes and use it as a blanket while lounging,relaxing at home or watching TV on the sofa. Will feel cozy all the day with this soft,warm heated blanket.
*USB Powered & Machine Washable*:This heated shawl is powered by any 5V 2A power supply and the pocket sewn inside it allows the power bank(not included) to be easily tucked in. Perfect for outdoor activities or travel in chill winter. Besides,it's machine washable for easy cleaning.
* Soft & Skin-Friendly*: Made of super soft polyester lining with short plush, the heated blanket is so soft, cozy, skin-friendly, and comfortable to wear that you won't want to take it off. Also come with two convenient pockets to keep your hand warm and allow you to fetch your cellphone,handbook,or other small items easily. An ideal gift for your families and friends to care for their health in cold winter.

Product Name: VEVOR Hanging Tree Tent, 330 LBS Capacity Hanging Tent Swing for Indoor and Outdoor Hammock Sensory Swing Chair w/LED Lights String, Inflatable Base, Ceiling Swing Pod Play Tent for Kids & Adults
Description:
Highlights:
1.Sturdy Hanging Tree Tent: Our hanging tree tent is crafted with 600D Oxford fabric, featuring multi-stitched top seams and thickened core ropes for tear-resistant durability. It boasts a high-strength steel frame with reinforced D-rings, supporting up to 330 lbs for maximum safety.
2.Upgraded Dual-layer Top: Our tree tent swing features innovative double waterproof layers that take your outdoor experience to the next level. The side curtains allow refreshing airflow, creating a comfortable and breezy environment inside.
3.Perfect Design: 5 interior pockets for convenient storage, an inflated bottom cushion, and four sponge-covered steel poles add comfort. The 4.92ft/1.5m thickened suspension rope is adjustable for versatile use. And the bottom-end fasteners and a four-hole circular ceiling mount with screws ensure extra stability.
4.Spacious Interior: Measuring 43x43x46 inch, the hanging tent is supported by three curved steel rods and can comfortably accommodate up to three children or one adult, offering ample space for various activities.
5.Versatile Usage: This hanging tent for kids provides a cozy space for reading, listening to music, playing games, watching videos, relaxing, and gently swinging. It can be used indoors in the living room, bedroom, or balcony, and outdoors in the courtyard, lawn, garden, or forests.

Details:
Swing into Comfort and Joy with VEVOR Hanging Tree Tent With a remarkable weight capacity of 330 lbs, our hanging tent swing offers a secure haven for both kids and adults. Reinforced with multi-stitched seams at the top and sturdy hanging rings, this hammock ensures stability and peace of mind, whether indoors or outdoors. VEVOR's ceiling swing hammock provides a comfortable resting space whether on rainy or sunny days. The upgraded double-layer waterproof top with the UV-resistant 600D Oxford fabric ensures a dry and enjoyable experience. Side windows keep fresh air circulation. This comfortable tree tent is equipped with a thick, removable inflatable cushion. It also boasts 5 interior pockets for storing personal items, keeping your space tidy. The built-in LED dreamy lights create a magical ambiance for your kids to revel in. The included large air pump simplifies setup, ideal for solo assembly. Just secure the circular ceiling with screws, insert sponge-shaping tubes and the inflatable cushion, hang the tent, and adjust the height – no extra tools are required! The 4.92ft/1.5m extended suspension rope allows flexible setup in various locations. Whether it's on a hammock stand, a tree branch, or a wooden or concrete ceiling, it adapts easily. With expansion bolts and woodworking screws, the setup is both stable and straightforward.

Product Name: Inflatable SUV Air Backseat Mattress Travel Pad with Pump Camping
Description:
Highlights:
1.Fast Inflation and Deflation: You can quickly inflate or deflate the airbed to desired firmness within minutes, and the firmness is adjustable according to your needs. To inflate the mattress, you can simply plug the pump into the car's cigarette lighter socket and pump air into the mattress with nozzles.
2.Soft and Durable Materials: This SUV air mattress features a comfortable flocking surface that is skin-friendly. The premium PVC bottom has tight stitches and doubles sealed air nozzles, ensuring this air mattress is completely airtight and won't easily crack. And it's easy to clean because of the waterproof design.
3.Practical 8 Compartments: This car air mattress can turn the back of your car into a comfortable bed and it has 8 separate airbags with independent air inlets. You can fully inflate the mattress for several people to use or partially inflate it for a single person. This comfortable air mattress helps you relax your body and enjoy better sleep on the go.
4.Versatile and Portable Design: This double-sided air mattress can be used as a resting bed whether you're in the car, outdoors or at home. Because of the inflatable design, the mattress can be folded quickly for storage and it's convenient to be taken out for travel and camping with the inclusive carry bag.
5.Fits for Different Models of Cars: This portable inflatable mattress is compatible with most car models and can be easily mounted on the rear seat. Folding part of the bags, this air bed can be placed at the rear seat with the help of an auxiliary airbag (not included). It is very suitable for SUV, hatchback, minivan or truck, etc.

Details:

Specifications

Overview
-Thickened mattress with the flocked surface for comfort sense of touch
-PVC material is durable and wear-resistant for long lifespan
-8 separate compartments with independent air inlets
-Fully or partially inflated to better fit the rear seat space and different situations
-Easy to inflate and deflate with electric air pump and nozzles included
-Foldable and portable air mattress for easily storing and carrying with a carry bag
-Ideal for SUVs, hatchbacks, limousines, trucks and so on
-Perfect for camping, road trip or placing at home for daily use
-Easy to clean with just a wipe

Product Name: Lightweight Sleeping Bag for Backpacking, Hiking, Waterproof Compact Envelope Sleeping Bag for Cold & Warm Weather, Blue
Description:
Details:

Introductions:
Experience the perfect balance of comfort and portability with this ultralight sleeping bag, designed for outdoor enthusiasts and casual campers alike. Crafted from a high-quality and durable 190T polyester shell, this envelope-style bag stands up to years of rugged use while remaining soft against the skin. It offers exceptional versatility, making it an ideal choice for backpacking, hiking, RV trips, or even crashing on a friend's couch. The waterproof outer shell ensures moisture stays out, keeping you dry and cozy throughout the night. With a weight of just 2.1 lbs, it is incredibly easy to carry without adding unnecessary bulk to your pack. Whether you are camping in the mountains or lounging in the backyard, this sleeping bag provides the warmth and reliability needed for a restful sleep in temperatures ranging from 42 to 68 °F.
Features:
1. High-Quality Durable Material: Constructed with a premium 190T polyester shell, this sleeping bag is built to withstand years of regular use. The waterproof outer layer offers excellent protection against moisture, ensuring a dry and comfortable experience during your outdoor adventures or indoor stays.
2. Optimal Temperature Control: Designed for versatility, this backpacking sleeping bag is suitable for a temperature range of 42 to 68 °F. It features an adjustable drawstring that allows you to tighten the bag around your neck, preserving body heat and providing extra warmth in colder weather.
3. Ultralight and Portable Design: Weighing only 2.1 lbs, this sleeping bag achieves the perfect balance of performance and lightweight convenience. It is specifically engineered for hiking and backpacking, making it easy to transport to the mountains, beach, or carry in your car and RV without weighing you down.
4. Secure and Accessible Usage: The bag is equipped with a smooth zipper mechanism secured with a velcro strap to prevent accidental opening while you sleep. This user-friendly design ensures you stay snug throughout the night, whether you are sleeping at the office, in the backyard, or at a campsite.
5. Easy Maintenance and Cleaning: Keeping your gear fresh is effortless as the waterproof shell can be easily wiped clean with a damp cloth to remove surface dirt. For deeper cleaning after heavy soilage, the sleeping bag is fully machine washable, ensuring long-lasting hygiene and durability for every trip.
Specifications:
1. Dimensions: (74.8 x 29.5) in / (190 x 75) cm
2. Weight: 2.1 lbs
3. Temperature Range: 42-68 °F

1 x Sleeping Bag

Description:

1.Innovator HD rooftop tent comes with multi-port USB outlet, upgraded adjustable luggage racks, full-circle led light strip with various brightness and 3-in-1 style with skyview window, regular and TPU rain flies.
2.Made from durable 320g polyester, aircraft-grade aluminum hardshell with aluminium round corners, STABILUS gas struts, waterproof rubber seal and flocked lining tent floor to prevent moisture.
3.Include a 3-layer built-in detachable mattress, YKK zipper netting windows, 13 interior ceiling&sidewall storage pouches, 7.68' extendable aluminum ladder and 2 detachable shoe storage bags.
4.Fit up to 2-3 adults with its spacious elevated design and pop up easily in just 5 seconds.
5.Compatible with nearly any vehicle equipped with proper cross bars. Requires cross bars with a dynamic weight load of at least 195 lbs.

C. 0.20" (0.5 cm) Ocean Mat: Absorbs moisture effectively, ensuring a dry and comfortable sleeping experience.

Product Name: VEVOR Portable Ice Shelter, 6-8 Person Pop-Up Ice Fishing Tent, 70 Square Feet Fishable Area, Ice Shanty for Winter Fishing, Waterproof Oxford Ice Cube with Anchors/Ropes/Carrying Bag, 142"x71" Black
Description:
Highlights:
1.Premium Fabric: This portable ice fishing shelter is made with high-quality 300D Oxford fabric and features a 3-layer PU black coating for excellent wind, water, and cold resistance. The strong light-blocking capability effectively prevents light penetration, enhancing your ice fishing experience and efficiency, creating an ideal environment for enthusiasts.
2.Stability in the Wind: The pop-up ice fishing tent's support rod structure is designed for durability and is reinforced at the corners with heavy-duty materials for superior wind and snow resistance. It includes 12 sturdy ice anchors and 6 wind ropes to ensure stability in strong winds. The ice anchors can be easily placed through the tie-down loops located on the extra-wide skirt.
3.Pop-up Design: The convenient pop-up design allows for easy setup and takedown of the ice shanty for winter fishing. With just a few simple steps, you can have your shelter ready for use or packed away quickly.
4.Additional Details: This 141.73x70.8x78.84 inch ice fishing shanty with carrying bag features a removable window design for adjustable ventilation and reduced leak risk. The zipper door design allows for easy entry and exit. An internal storage bag provides convenient organization for various items, enhancing your comfort and enjoyment during winter fishing.
5.Easy to Carry: This quick-open foldable ice fishing tent is lightweight and easy to carry, making it simple to store. You can pack everything into a large tote bag with backpack straps for convenient transport. Start your ice fishing adventure anytime, anywhere, and enjoy great convenience for outdoor enthusiasts.

Details:
Pop-Up Portable Ice Fishing Tent This ice fishing tent is made of 300D Oxford fabric, providing exceptional windproof effects, staying stable even in snow and wind. The spacious interior can accommodate 6-8 people. The tent is easy to set up and take down, portable, and easy to store. This portable ice shelter features a convenient double zipper and double-door design, allowing easy access while maintaining excellent visibility. The four-window design offers superior ventilation, ensuring a comfortable experience during your ice fishing trips. This multi-person ice fishing shanty offers a spacious interior suitable for 6-8 people. Its multi-functional use meets your needs, whether for outdoor ice fishing, winter camping, temporary outdoor shelter, or covering and protecting equipment in cold weather. This ice shanty for winter fishing includes a tent, ice anchors, wind ropes, and a portable carrying bag. The tent's design is stable, with ice anchors ensuring stability. Enjoy fishing or outdoor adventures, staying protected from cold and snow while having fun. This ice shelter fishing tent is specially designed for outdoor ice fishing enthusiasts, suitable for various scenes such as winter outdoors, backyards, outdoor areas, and lakes. It can be quickly set up, allowing you to enjoy a warm, cozy space in no time.

Product Name: VEVOR Canvas Bell Tent, 4 Seasons 6 m/19.68 ft Yurt Tent, Canvas Tent for Camping with Stove Jack, Breathable Tent Holds up to 10 People, Family Camping Outdoor Hunting Party
Description:
Highlights:
1.Durable Materials: Made from TC cotton canvas (65% polyester and 35% cotton blend), our canvas bell tent is durable, waterproof, and breathable, suitable for light to moderate rain conditions. Additional waterproof cover is recommended for heavy rain or storms. The ground mat is a special thick mat made from 540gsm waterproof PVC, offering snow and wind resistance to keep you dry and comfortable.
2.Comfortable Experience: The 5" stove hole, made from flame-resistant material, features a 43x43cm flap, allowing safe indoor heating. Four mesh-covered windows offer excellent ventilation and bug protection during the summer. Roll-up canvas and mesh keep critters out while letting cool breezes in for a peaceful sleep.
3.Spacious Interior: With a 6 m/19.68 ft diameter, our bell tent comfortably accommodates up to 10 people, providing ample room for family, friends, or group camping, giving you plenty of space to move around.
4.Easy Setup: Enjoy the outdoor camping in just 4 simple steps. The canvas tent comes with 14 nylon reflective ropes and 14 aluminum alloy rope tensioners to secure it to prevent blowing down, ensuring your camping experience is safe.
5.Convenient Portability: The yurt tent includes a rain cap, ground stakes, a stake hammer, a tent bag, and storage bags with handles for easy transportation and storage. Whether it's spring, summer, fall, or winter, this tent is your reliable companion for outdoor adventures.

Details:
VEVOR Canvas Bell Tent for Ultimate Camping Comfort Perfect for outdoor adventures! Our bell tent is crafted from breathable TC cotton canvas (65% polyester and 35% cotton blend), ideal for light to moderate rain. For heavy rain or storms, add an extra waterproof cover. The ground mat offers snow and wind resistance for comfort and dryness. Experience unmatched camping comfort! This canvas tent comes equipped with a stove jack, allowing you to stay warm during chilly winter nights. It has four windows and mesh doors, allowing you to appreciate the beauty of the night sky. You can even use it as a canopy to get even closer to nature. This canvas bell tent offers ample interior space for you and your family to embrace the great outdoors and relish outdoor living. It comfortably accommodates multiple people, providing plenty of room to move around and relax in the lap of nature. Setting up the bell tent is a breeze with just four simple steps. We also provide a camping tool kit, complete with stakes and a hammer, ensuring the tent's safety and stability. You can easily assemble it in no time, leaving you more time to enjoy your camping trip. Our yurt tent not only offers a convenient living space but also adds convenience to your travels. Multiple storage bags make it easy to organize and store tent accessories without losing them.

Product Name: VEVOR Camping Shower Tent, 66" x 66" x 87" 1 Room Oversize Outdoor Portable Shelter, Privacy Tent with Detachable Top, Pockets, Hanging Rope and Clothesline, for Dressing, Changing, Toilet, Bathroom
Description:
Highlights:
1.Privacy in the Wild: Do you here the call from nature? Amid the call of the great outdoors, your security and privacy are our top concerns. This camping shower tent is made of thickened Oxford fabric and a fiberglass frame to withstand harsh outdoor conditions. Completed with side windows and various storage designs, it provides you with the security and convenience of a home bathroom.
2.Take on Tough Conditions: Our outdoor shower tent is crafted from a combination of 190T polyester and 210D Oxford fabric. It offers UV50 protection to shield you from the scorching sun, while the two windows provide proper ventilation to prevent stuffiness. In addition, the tent has a waterproof rating of PU2000mm, which ensures rainwater slides off quickly without penetrating the tent.
3.Feel Just Like Home: The storage design of our shower tents for camping provides convenience and comfort like a home bathroom. From the clothesline for clothes and towels, ceiling cords for hanging lights and showerheads, to two storage bags and hooks for essentials, it ensures convenience and comfort for temporary outdoor showers and changing.
4.Shower in Comfort: We have made significant improvements to our shower tent, ensuring high quality in every detail. Our smooth SBS zippers allow for easy access, while the storage bag makes packing up a breeze. The button system makes securing the door effortlessly, and the mesh windows provide excellent ventilation. All of these features are designed to offer you a comfortable and private space.
5.Multifunctional Tent: This privacy tent measures 66" x 66" x 87", providing plenty of space to move around comfortably during showers. It provides good ventilation when used as a mobile toilet. Additionally, when shooting outdoors, it serves as a temporary dressing room, making it convenient to change clothes and store garments.

Details:
Multifunctional Outdoor Shower Tent Ready to enjoy the outdoors? Our shower tent is made of extra-thick Oxford fabric, providing unmatched privacy protection. It has a spacious size of 66" x 66" x 87", which allows for comfortable standing and stretching. Stay clean, refreshed, and ready to continue your adventure with VEVOR! Our shower tent for camping adopts polyester and 210D Oxford fabric, which is waterproof and sun-proof. It ensures non-light penetration for absolute privacy. Thanks to the side windows and top opening, you'll enjoy delightful ventilation even in summer. Our tent stands out from regular shower tents with its user-friendly storage upgrade. It includes side pockets and hooks that make it easy to store small items, and the top cord and clothesline allow for hanging clothing. These features address common challenges encountered during outdoor showering. This portable shower tent showcases excellence in every detail. From the smooth SBS zippers, handy storage bag, and easy-to-use buttons to the mesh windows, each element provides a comfortable and convenient space for you. Whether you're camping outdoors and require a temporary toilet and quick shower space, or you're conducting an outdoor photoshoot needing a dressing room, this privacy tent provides the perfect solution.

Product Name: 2000W Double Electric Burner Portable Dual Counter Stove Countertop Hot Plate Kitchen Cooker Stove with 5 Gear Temperature Control
Description:
Details:

Is your cooking space compromised? Our Portable Double Hot Plate can save your space and give you mighty 2000W capacity to ensure maximum heat for quick heating with 5 temperature gears. Compact size allows it to be used in dorms, offices, or even carry for travel. Perfect for boiling water, reheating sauces, making soups to meet your daily needs!

Heat Quickly & Evenly: Equipped with double 6in burning plates and powered by 2000W of powerful power, it heats up quickly and cooks food evenly without any hot or cold spots.
5 Power Levels: With 1-5 heating temperature adjustment, easily meet your daily cooking needs, such as boiling water, reheating sauces, making soups, frying steak, cooking pasta, grilling cheese and vegetables, etc.. Independent adjustable thermostat controls and indicator lights for convenient operation.
Safe Using & Easy Cleaning: With safety overheat protection, automatic safety cut off. Just simply wipe the non-electrical parts with a damp sponge or wet cloth for easy cleaning after cooling down completely.
Wide Compatibility: The burner can be used with any flat-bottomed cookware made of a variety of materials, such as frying pans, woks or stovetop teapots made from aluminum, stainless steel, iron or glass. Note: May heat ceramic pot very slowly.
Compact Design: With compact design of 16.93x8.27x2.56in, occupies small space, perfect use in student dorms, offices, campsites, RVs and home. Also ideal for travel using.

Warm Tips:
1. When cooking, someone’s better look at it.
2. Do not touch the surface of the heating pan during heating.
3. Do not immerse the hot plate into the water or other liquids.
4. The hot plate is to heat food, when cooking food the container should be on the heating plate.
5. When the hot plate is not in use, be sure to adjust the switch to the 'off' position and unplug the plug.
6. When using the hot plate for the first time, it should be adjusted to the third level for 3-5 minutes to evaporate the protective film of the furnace surface. At this time, there may be a small amount of smoke emitted, which is normal. It won\'t happen when use next time.
7. The utensils placed on the hot plate must have a smooth bottom and a diameter that matches the size of the hot plate.
8. If the size of the cooking vessel chassis is smaller than the size of the electric heating plate, it will affect the normal heating area of the heating plate.
9. If the bottom of the vessel is not flat, it can’t be used with the concave and convex situation.
10. When using, do not place other sundries within 30cm/11.81in around the hot plate to prevent blockage and ventilation.

Over-Heating Protection:
When reaches the corresponding max temperature, the Hot Plate will auto cut off electricity and the indicator will turn off, too. After it cools down and works again, the indicator will turn on again.
* For first gear: ≥160℃/320℉
* For second gear: ≥280℃/536℉
* For third gear: ≥420℃/788℉
* For fourth gear: ≥560℃/1040℉
* For fifth gear: ≥600℃/1112℉
* The hot plate can reach up to 500℃/932℉

*2 in 1 Portable Heater & Stove*:Our camping gas stove combines a burner and a grate to serve the purpose of cooking and heating for your outdoor adventures. suitable for camping,fishing,ice fishing,picnic,hunting,hiking,traveling,etc..

2. Please turn off the stove before sleep.
3. Please keep it away from children

Product Name: 7-Person 1-Room Teepee Tent;  with Vented Rear Window;  Green
Description:
Highlights:
1.Be the talk of the campground or music festival with the 7-Person Teepee Tent with Vented Rear Window.
2.This fun tent, with its nostalgic teepee design, has a unique frame that eliminates the center support pole and sleeps up to seven people.
3.With 105 square feet of living space and a 92-inch center height, this tent is as spacious as it is fun to camp in.
4.For 2021, weve redesigned our Teepee and added a screened window to the front door to improve airflow while keeping the bugs out. This window along with two side windows provide great cross-ventilation. Three peak vents and a new vented rear window provide high-low air circulation and reduce condensation inside the tent.
5.Storage pockets keep small items off the floor and the tent tidy. An E-port provides easy electrical cord access and a media pocket provides a family viewing area. Take the 7-Person Teepee Tent with Vented Rear Window on your next camping outing with friends and fun will be unavoidable!

Product Name: VEVOR Camping Folding Chair for Adults, Portable Heavy Duty Outdoor Quad Lumbar Back Padded Arm Chairs with Side Pockets, Cup Holder and Cooler Bag for Beach, Lawn, Picnic, Fishing, Backpacking, Black
Description:
Highlights:
1.Premium 600D Oxford Fabric: Made with 600D rip-stop Oxford fabric, this camping chair is tearing-resistant and abrasion-proof, making it ideal for camping, fishing, and BBQ. The backrest features 200g/m solid cotton padding for lasting support
2.Heavy-Duty 450 Lbs Load: Built for strength, these folding camping chairs support up to 450 lbs / 204 kg. The reinforced steel frame, thickened steel tubes, and X-shaped structure ensure stability, rust-resistance, and long-term durability
3.Comfortable Seating: This camping folding chair features solid cotton padding in the backrest and armrests. With a 22.6 in high back, 24.0 in seat depth, and 24.4 in seat width, the wide high-back supports the waist and follows natural body contour
4.Multi-Functional Storage Pockets: Designed for convenience, these foldable camping chairs include a left armrest cooler bag (fits 6 cans), a right-side cup holder, a side pocket, and a front magazine pocket for drinks, snacks, phones, and accessories
5.Lightweight & Portable: This camp chair is lightweight and can be lifted easily with one hand. When folded, it is portable and comes with one carry bag, ideal for solo outdoor activities and compact trunk storage, making transport quick wherever you go

Details:
Outdoor Camping Companion From rugged trails to quiet lakesides, BBQs to music festivals, this outdoor folding chair series offers reliable support for any setting. Built with industrial-grade durability and ergonomic design, it delivers stable support and lasting comfort wherever you go. Solid cotton filling follows the natural spine curve, replacing thin padding. The deep seat offers ample leg support, while supportive armrests assist standing. The design of the lawn chairs helps reduce lower back pressure for relaxed fishing or stargazing. The camping chair series uses high-density 600D ripstop Oxford fabric or polyester fabric with surface treatment to handle abrasion, liquid splashes, and repeated folding. Q195 iron or carbon steel tubing with a cross-support structure and reinforced welding supports long-term use. These heavy duty lawn chairs focus on practical outdoor use, featuring a left armrest cooling ice pack for up to six cans and a right armrest cup holder for standard drink containers. Front and side pockets store snacks, maps, phones, and small items. Designed for outdoor users on the move, this camping folding chair features a quick folding structure that reduces thickness after storage. A high-density Oxford fabric carry bag is included. The folded shape fits car trunk spaces and allows setup directly after unfolding.

Product Name: Lightweight Sleeping Bag for Backpacking, Hiking, Waterproof Compact Envelope Sleeping Bag for Cold & Warm Weather, Red
Description:
Details:

Introductions:
Experience the perfect balance of comfort and portability with this ultralight sleeping bag, designed for outdoor enthusiasts and casual campers alike. Crafted from a high-quality and durable 190T polyester shell, this envelope-style bag stands up to years of rugged use while remaining soft against the skin. It offers exceptional versatility, making it an ideal choice for backpacking, hiking, RV trips, or even crashing on a friend's couch. The waterproof outer shell ensures moisture stays out, keeping you dry and cozy throughout the night. With a weight of just 2.1 lbs, it is incredibly easy to carry without adding unnecessary bulk to your pack. Whether you are camping in the mountains or lounging in the backyard, this sleeping bag provides the warmth and reliability needed for a restful sleep in temperatures ranging from 42 to 68 °F.
Features:
1. High-Quality Durable Material: Constructed with a premium 190T polyester shell, this sleeping bag is built to withstand years of regular use. The waterproof outer layer offers excellent protection against moisture, ensuring a dry and comfortable experience during your outdoor adventures or indoor stays.
2. Optimal Temperature Control: Designed for versatility, this backpacking sleeping bag is suitable for a temperature range of 42 to 68 °F. It features an adjustable drawstring that allows you to tighten the bag around your neck, preserving body heat and providing extra warmth in colder weather.
3. Ultralight and Portable Design: Weighing only 2.1 lbs, this sleeping bag achieves the perfect balance of performance and lightweight convenience. It is specifically engineered for hiking and backpacking, making it easy to transport to the mountains, beach, or carry in your car and RV without weighing you down.
4. Secure and Accessible Usage: The bag is equipped with a smooth zipper mechanism secured with a velcro strap to prevent accidental opening while you sleep. This user-friendly design ensures you stay snug throughout the night, whether you are sleeping at the office, in the backyard, or at a campsite.
5. Easy Maintenance and Cleaning: Keeping your gear fresh is effortless as the waterproof shell can be easily wiped clean with a damp cloth to remove surface dirt. For deeper cleaning after heavy soilage, the sleeping bag is fully machine washable, ensuring long-lasting hygiene and durability for every trip.
Specifications:
1. Dimensions: (74.8 x 29.5) in / (190 x 75) cm
2. Weight: 2.1 lbs
3. Temperature Range: 42-68 °F

1 x Sleeping Bag

Product Name: 8 Person Clip & Camp Family Tent
Description:
Highlights:
1.The 8 Person Clip & Camp Family Tent is the perfect tent for all your outdoor needs. This tent is easy to set up and fits in most camping spaces. The unique enlarged dome design allows for a more comfortable headroom while still maintaining that great low profile.
2.Enough room to easily fit a queen-sized air mattress with extra room to store your gear and other needed camping items. The built-in mud mat at the entrance helps to keep your tent clean of dirt and other debris and speaking of built-ins, your tent also includes other useful built-in features, such as the footlocker at the side of the entrance.
3.Along with a rainfly that protects you from inclement weather, this tent went the extra step and seam-taped the fly to further support the already water-resistant rainfly.
4.Your rainfly also doubles as a protective awning over the large D-shaped door. The ability to create airflow in the ways you want it. Keep it closed on cooler nights to lock-in that comfy body warmth or open it up on warm summer nights to feel that cool breeze zipping through.
5.The rainfly can also be detached and underneath you will notice the brilliant full mesh roof design, perfect for looking up at the vast night sky while you peacefully fall asleep.

Details:



Product details
The 8 Person Clip & Camp Family Tent is the perfect tent for all your outdoor needs. This tent is easy to set up and fits in most camping spaces. The unique enlarged dome design allows for a more comfortable headroom while still maintaining that great low profile. Enough room to easily fit a queen-sized air mattress with extra room to store your gear and other needed camping items. The built-in mud mat at the entrance helps to keep your tent clean of dirt and other debris and speaking of built-ins; your tent also includes other useful built-in features; such as the footlocker at the side of the entrance. Along with a rainfly that protects you from inclement weather; this tent went the extra step and seam-taped the fly to further support the already water-resistant rainfly. Your rainfly also doubles as a protective awning over the large D-shaped door. The ability to create airflow in the ways you want it. Keep it closed on cooler nights to lock-in that comfy body warmth or open it up on warm summer nights to feel that cool breeze zipping through. The rainfly can also be detached and underneath you will notice the brilliant full mesh roof design; perfect for looking up at the vast night sky while you peacefully fall asleep. Product Name: 2-in-1 Folding Fish Cleaning Table
Description:
Highlights:
1.2-in-1 Fish Cleaning Table: This fish cleaning table with a spray nozzle included can help you clean food with higher efficiency. Also, the 2 sinks can be covered and the faucet can be detached, turning it into a patio picnic table. Such a 2-in-1 multifunctional design makes this fish table perfect for camping, fishing and picnic.
2.Functional Double Sinks: The 2 sinks with a 360 rotatable faucet in the middle will satisfy your different demands. One side can be used for washing and another side is perfect for cooling food. Moreover, the faucet can be folded when not in use. And the drainage hole with a plug helps you discharge water quickly.
3.High Stability and Durability: The tabletop is made of weatherproof HDPE with a thickness of up to 3". And the table leg with triangular support feature is constructed of sturdy metal, ensuring strong support up to 330lbs. Moreover, the anti-slip footpads protect the ground from scratches and improve overall stability.
4.Easy to Store and Transport: The quick-folding design with safety latch allows you to effortlessly carry or store the folded table which measures only 40" x 26" x 5" (L x W x H). Plus, the telescoping drain pipes can be extended from 13" to 33.5" as you need.
5.Offer More Convenience: The scale for measurement on the table enables you to clearly know the size of material. The garbage holder cut-out is effective to make the tabletop well organized. Also, the 4 knife grooves are perfect to place knives for higher safety. And the round corner avoids any stitches or injuries.

Product Name: Inflatable Waterproof Camping Pad for Outdoor Travel

Highlights:
1.This camping mattress folds down to a tiny size that fits easily into your backpack or suitcase.
2.Crafted from high-quality 20D nylon and inner TPU coating, this inflatable mattress has good performance in tear resistance, wear resistance and waterproofness.
3.The waterproof surface keeps camping mattress dry and saves much effort in daily maintenance.
4.This camping mattress can be rolled up into a compact size and fixed by straps and buckles, making it easy to store while saving much space.
5.Suitable for hiking or road trip, have a picnic, or enjoy a beach bath, this mattress is clearly the ideal choice for you to sit and sleep.

Description:
Highlights:
1.1 - Aluminium Hard Shell with Aluminium Round Corner and Stainless Steel Gas Struts: Durable and built to endure the ever-changing season.
2.2 - Side Awning: Offer extra shade and protection from the sun and rain, perfect for enjoying the outdoors.
3.3 - Bulit-in USB Outlet for you to charge outside
4.4 - Replaceable Rain Flies/Rain Curtains: Allow you to easily replace the rain fly/rain curtain, ensuring flexibility and long-lasting protection.
5.5 - 3 Layer Luxurious Mattress, Upgraded with Flocked Lining Tent Floor to Prevent Condensation with 6 - 3 Layer Luxurious Mattress, Upgraded with Flocked Lining Tent Floor to Prevent Condensation

Details:

About this item

1. Polyester, Nylon Mesh, Black Vinyl Coating

2.[Upgraded Rooftop Tent Hardshell to 100% Market Excellence] - HEYFUN roof top tent RTT, directly from the industry-leading manufacturer, are standout options with premium features including multi-port USB outlet, extra attachable side awning, replaceable netting rain curtain and adjustable luggage racks, best travel solution for carrying more luggage and perfect choice for camping enthusiasts and seasoned adventurers of all levels valuing quality and affordability.

3. [Aluminum Rooftop Tent with 3 Layer Mattress&YKK Zipper] - The SUV car roof tent is designed with durable 320g polyester, aircraft-grade aluminum hardshell, stainless steel gas struts, waterproof sealing gaskets, moisture-proof flocked lining tent floor, 3-layer built-in detachable mattress, YKK zipper netting windows&windproof layers, 13 interior ceiling&sidewall storage pouches and aluminum ladder, providing strength&rigidity, UV-resistant and breathable.

4. 5. [Pop up Overland Tent with 5 Seconds to Open and Close] - The hydraulic automatic top tent with rust-resistant&corrosion-resistant stainless steel gas struts and dual buckles, easily pop up or put away in 5 seconds, can be used continuously for many years without losing stability and safety for Truck Jeep SUV Car Van Wrangler Tacoma Minivan, making overlanding easy and hassle-free.

6. [4-Season Offroad Roof Tent in the Wooden Package] - This rugged all-weather outdoor roof top tent, packed in a sturdy wooden box with pre-assembled accessories, ensures safe delivery without damage and easy setup for first-time users. It withstands the elements, resists aging, heat&cold, provides excellent ventilation in summer, and retains warmth in winter, making it the ideal all-season camping tent for year-round adventures.

7. [HEYFUN Tent Warranty for 2 Years] - Truck Bed & Tailgate Bed Tents: 30-day money-back guarantee for product returns. 2-year limited warranty on manufacturer's defects from the purchase date, excluding damage resulting from misuse. Dry the rooftop tent completely before storing it after rainy use.

Product Name: VEVOR Car Side Awning, Large 4.6'x6.6' Shade Coverage Vehicle Awning, PU3000mm UV50+ Retractable Car Awning with Waterproof Storage Bag, Suitable for Truck, SUV, Van, Campers
Description:
Highlights:
1.Expansive Coverage: Our large 4.6x6.6 ft car side awning provides complete sunshade, effectively shielding you from UV rays. Its windproof and waterproof design ensures you stay protected in any weather. It comfortably accommodates 3-5 people for various activities.
2.Heavy-Duty & Durable Material: Crafted from 280G polyester fabric with a PU 3000mm coating, the vehicle awning is dense and durable. The rust-proof aluminum alloy support poles with reinforced corners, and rubber connectors are designed for added strength. Thickeded wind-resistant ropes are ready to withstand all weather conditions.
3.Sunproof, Waterproof & Windproof: Featuring a black sunshade coating, waterproof layer, and heat-insulating design, our car awning excels in sunshade, waterproofing, insulation, durability, and UV resistance. Say goodbye to heat build-up and rainwater seepage for a cool and dry camping experience.
4.User-Friendly Design: Professional-grade luminous ground pegs ensure visibility at night and prevent tripping. Our SUV awning comes with a waterproof PVC carry bag for space-saving storage and portability. Plus, it's a breeze to install, even for beginners.
5.Versatile Compatibility: This truck awning effortlessly fits various vehicles with roof racks, luggage carriers, and more. Whether you attach it to the side or rear of your vehicle or use the steel poles as a ground shelter, it offers ample space and a stable structure, perfect for camping, picnics, family gatherings, or road trips.

Details:
4.6x6.6 ft Retractable Car Side Awning Our portable vehicle awning provides a spacious 4.6x6.6 ft shelter with UV protection, windproof, waterproof, and heat insulation. It comes with a PVC bag for space-saving car roof placement. Fits both the side and rear of your vehicle, providing shelter for picnics and camping in all weathers. Thickened aluminum alloy support poles, four reinforced corners and rubber connectors all ensure a robust and sturdy construction. Along with thick wind-resistant ropes, this car awning ensures stability even on windy days. With rotating locking designs on both the horizontal and vertical support poles, it allows for width and height adjustments, increasing flexibility and providing a quick and easy setup and disassembly. With overall dimensions of 61x6x2.8 inch/155×15×7 cm, our bag won't occupy much space on your vehicle roof. The PVC material offers excellent waterproofing, without worry about rainwater seepage even during rainy days. Comes with installation instructions to help you set up quickly. You can position the truck awning according to your outdoor needs. Complete installation in just 3-5 minutes, saving you both time and effort.

Product Name: 3 People Sleeping Bag for Adult Kids Lightweight Water Resistant Camping Cotton Liner Cold Warm Weather Indoor Outdoor Use 3 Season with Sack for Spring Summer Autumn
Description:
Highlights:
1.Creates a relaxing and reassuring sleep after a hard day of activities with smooth zippers and premium hollow cotton
2.Made of two layers of quilts with two snug-free removable zippers at the edge of the sleeping bag
3.Easy to store and carry anytime you want to start a backpacking, camping, hiking and trekking trip
4.The cotton stuffing keeps you warm and cozy
5.Clean with a damp cloth and designed for machine washing

Details:
*Features*:
*Good night’s Sleep*:Creates a relaxing and reassuring sleep after a hard day of activities with smooth zippers and premium hollow cotton. The envelope structure provides a built-in soft pillow and a flexible stretching space,which makes you feel at home. Moreover,two fasten straps at both sides prevent any unwanted zipper opening when you sleep.
*Versatile Sleeping Bag*:Made of two layers of quilts with two snug-free removable zippers at the edge of the sleeping bag,which offers two different ways to tuck in. You can share the bed with each other or unzip it to change it into two single sleeping bags.
*Camping Companion*:Lightweight with a carry bag,easy to store and carry anytime you want to start a backpacking,camping,hiking and trekking trip.
*3 Seasons Sleeping Bag*:Perfect for spring,summer and autumn with a temperature range from 50°F to 69.8°F(2 People);37.4°F -69.8°F(3 People). The cotton stuffing keeps you warm and cozy. Product Name: 8PC 12inch Strong Fixation, Threaded Steel Ground Screws. Versatile for Pipe and Tent Fixing. Durable and Windproof.
Description:
Highlights:
1.High-Strength Threaded Steel: Durable threaded steel with strong tensile strength ensures long-term stability in a variety of outdoor environments.
2.Threaded Design: The unique thread structure increases friction with the soil, ensuring the ground screws firmly grip the ground and prevent objects from sliding or shifting.
3.Versatile Applications: Suitable for a variety of applications, including pipe fixing, tent support, and tarpaulin fixing, helping you easily solve your outdoor fixing problems.
4.Wind and Water Resistant: Strong fixings resist loosening even in strong winds or heavy rain, ensuring your tent or pipe remains secure in extreme weather.
5.Easy to Use: The simple design allows for easy insertion into the soil without the need for additional tools or complicated operations, saving time and effort for a quick and convenient installation.

Details:

Made of high-strength threaded steel, these ground screws are engineered to secure pipes, tents, tarpaulins, and other items in various soil environments, preventing them from shifting or tilting due to wind or external impact. Their threaded design enhances friction with the soil, providing a secure hold. They're perfect for camping, outdoor activities, gardening, and more, making them an essential fixing tool.

Category: Outdoor>>Camping & Hiking>>Tents & Accessories>>Multiple Person 3 Or 4 Season Expedition Tents
Product Name: VEVOR Canvas Tent, 4 Seasons 5 m/16.4 ft Bell Tent, Canvas Tent for Camping with Stove Jack, Breathable Yurt Tent for up to 8 People, Family Camping Outdoor Hunting Party
Description:
Highlights:
1.Durable Materials: Made of TC (Technical Cotton) fabric, our tent offers excellent durability and breathability, helping reduce interior condensation and making it suitable for year-round use. (Note: The cotton material provides limited insulation, so please use with caution in extreme heat or cold.) Sturdy galvanized iron center and door poles ensure reliable stability.
2.Comfortable Experience: This bell tent offers 3 usage modes - full mode, rolled-up door mode, or groundless canopy mode, allowing you to experience the beauty of nature up close. It also features a 3.9" stove hole, keeping you warm on chilly winter days. Eight mesh-covered windows provide excellent ventilation and keep critters out in summer.
3.Spacious Interior: With a diameter of up to 5 m/16.4 ft and a wall height of 1.4 m/4.59 ft, our canvas bell tent comfortably accommodates up to 8 people, providing ample room for family, friends, or group camping, giving you plenty of space to move around.
4.Easy Setup: Enjoy the outdoor camping in just 4 simple steps. The yurt tent comes with 8 nylon reflective ropes and 16 ground stakes to to secure it to prevent blowing down, ensuring your camping experience is safe.
5.Convenient Portability: The camping bell tent includes a rain cap, ground stakes, a stake hammer, a tent bag, and storage bags with handles for easy transportation and storage. Whether it's spring, summer, fall, or winter, this tent is your reliable companion for outdoor adventures.

Details:
VEVOR Canvas Bell Tent for Ultimate Camping Comfort Perfect for outdoor adventures! Our bell tent is crafted from breathable TC cotton canvas (65% polyester and 35% cotton blend), ideal for light to moderate rain. For heavy rain or storms, add an extra waterproof cover. The waterproof Oxford tent wall and ground mat ensure comfort and dryness. Experience unmatched camping comfort! This canvas tent comes equipped with a stove jack, allowing you to stay warm during chilly winter nights. It has 8 mesh windows, allowing you to appreciate the beauty of the night sky. You can even use it as a canopy to get even closer to nature. This canvas bell tent offers ample interior space with a diameter of 5m/16.4ft for you and your family to embrace the great outdoors and relish outdoor living. It comfortably accommodates up to 8 people, providing plenty of room to move around and relax in the lap of nature. Setting up the bell tent is a breeze with just four simple steps. We also provide a camping tool kit, complete with stakes and a hammer, ensuring the tent's safety and stability. You can easily assemble it in no time, leaving you more time to enjoy your camping trip. Our yurt tent not only offers a convenient living space but also adds convenience to your travels. Multiple storage bags make it easy to organize and store tent accessories without losing them.

Product Name: Rectangular Heated Sleeping Bag, Lightweight Sleeping Bag with Multi USB Powered Heating Pads, Waterproof Compact Envelope Sleeping Bag for Backpacking Hiking, Green
Description:
Details:

Introductions:
Stay warm and comfortable during your outdoor adventures with this innovative rectangular heated sleeping bag. Designed for versatility, it features a built-in electronic heating system powered by USB, allowing you to connect it easily to power banks or other USB power sources. The outer shell is crafted from high-quality, durable 190T polyester, making it waterproof and tough enough to withstand years of regular use while remaining soft against the skin. Whether you are camping in the mountains, relaxing at the beach, or needing a quick nap at the office, this bag ensures a restful experience. It includes a smooth zipper secured with velcro and an adjustable drawstring hood to trap heat effectively. Despite its advanced heating capabilities, the bag remains ultralight and portable, offering the perfect balance of warmth and convenience for hiking, backpacking, and RV travel.
Features:
1. Multi-Zone Electronic Heating: Equipped with a 4-piece heating pad 3D system, this sleeping bag targets key areas including the shoulder, chest, hip, and feet. The system is compatible with various USB power supplies such as cellphone chargers, power banks, and car jump starters, providing consistent warmth where you need it most.
2. Adjustable Temperature Control: This heated sleeping bag offers three distinct levels of heating to suit your comfort needs. You can easily adjust the settings to warm your body during chilly nights or lower the temperature mode if you feel too hot, making it suitable for use across all seasons.
3. Durable and Waterproof Material: Constructed with a high-quality 190T polyester shell, this bag is designed to stand up to years of rugged outdoor use. The waterproof exterior protects against moisture and damp conditions, ensuring you stay dry and comfortable whether you are in a tent or sleeping under the stars.
4. Secure Heat Retention Design: Features a smooth zipper secured with a velcro strap and a drawstring hood for precise adjustment. By tugging the drawstrings, you can bring the headrest closer to your body, sealing in warmth and providing extra insulation against cold air during lower temperatures.
5. Ultralight and Versatile Usage: Weighing only 3.3 lbs, this sleeping bag is easy to carry and perfect for backpacking, hiking, and camping. Its versatile design makes it an excellent choice for sleeping at home, in the office, backyard, car, or RV, balancing high performance with lightweight materials.
Specifications:
1. Dimensions: (82.7 x 33.5) in / (210 x 85) cm
2. Weight: 3.3 lbs
3. Temperature Range: 14-50 °F
Package Includes:
1 x Sleeping Bag

Product Name: Outsunny Smokeless Fire Pit, 19" Portable Wood Burning Firepit with Poker, Low Smoke Camping Bonfire Stove for Backyard Patio Picnic, Stainless Steel, Bronze
Description:
Details:

Product Features:
Smokeless Fire Pit: Keep comfortable when you camp when you finally say goodbye to smoke in your eyes. Our wood-burning, smokeless fire pit lets you enjoy warmth and ambiance without any discomfort.
Secondary Combustion: This smokeless camping fire pit uses a "secondary combustion" process. Bottom vents feed your fire fresh oxygen from below
this oxygen is heated as it rises up the walls, causing conditions that allow smoke to burn away, resulting in clean, smokeless fire.
Poker Included: Thoughtfully included is an added fire wood poker. Move logs used for fuel around our round fire pit to ensure a burn-free camping trip while easily maintaining an optimal flame.
Patio Ready: Made to endure heat and weather, such as rain, our stainless steel patio fire pit is built to provide you with warm, cozy, smokeless fire season after season.

Product Name: Rectangular Heated Sleeping Bag, Lightweight Sleeping Bag with Multi USB Powered Heating Pads, Waterproof Compact Envelope Sleeping Bag for Backpacking Hiking, Blue
Description:
Details:

Introductions:
Stay warm and comfortable during your outdoor adventures with this innovative rectangular heated sleeping bag. Designed for versatility, it features a built-in electronic heating system powered by USB, allowing you to connect it easily to power banks or other USB power sources. The outer shell is crafted from high-quality, durable 190T polyester, making it waterproof and tough enough to withstand years of regular use while remaining soft against the skin. Whether you are camping in the mountains, relaxing at the beach, or needing a quick nap at the office, this bag ensures a restful experience. It includes a smooth zipper secured with velcro and an adjustable drawstring hood to trap heat effectively. Despite its advanced heating capabilities, the bag remains ultralight and portable, offering the perfect balance of warmth and convenience for hiking, backpacking, and RV travel.
Features:
1. Multi-Zone Electronic Heating: Equipped with a 4-piece heating pad 3D system, this sleeping bag targets key areas including the shoulder, chest, hip, and feet. The system is compatible with various USB power supplies such as cellphone chargers, power banks, and car jump starters, providing consistent warmth where you need it most.
2. Adjustable Temperature Control: This heated sleeping bag offers three distinct levels of heating to suit your comfort needs. You can easily adjust the settings to warm your body during chilly nights or lower the temperature mode if you feel too hot, making it suitable for use across all seasons.
3. Durable and Waterproof Material: Constructed with a high-quality 190T polyester shell, this bag is designed to stand up to years of rugged outdoor use. The waterproof exterior protects against moisture and damp conditions, ensuring you stay dry and comfortable whether you are in a tent or sleeping under the stars.
4. Secure Heat Retention Design: Features a smooth zipper secured with a velcro strap and a drawstring hood for precise adjustment. By tugging the drawstrings, you can bring the headrest closer to your body, sealing in warmth and providing extra insulation against cold air during lower temperatures.
5. Ultralight and Versatile Usage: Weighing only 3.3 lbs, this sleeping bag is easy to carry and perfect for backpacking, hiking, and camping. Product Name: VEVOR Outdoor Oven 12-inch Pellet and Charcoal Fired Maker, Portable Outside Stainless Steel Grill with Pizza Stone, Waterproof Cover, Shovel, Wood Burner for Backyard Camping, Black
Description:
Highlights:
1.Bake Like Never Before: Are you tired of pizza ovens that just don't do what they are supposed to? Our outdoor pizza oven heats up to 1000Fahrenheit/540Celsius in just 30 minutes and bakes a tasty 12-inch pizza in 90 seconds or less! Plus, it's versatile enough to cook all kinds of meats, fish, and delicious vegetables.

5.Become a Chef in No Time: Ready to use straight out of the box! Simply fill the fuel tray with wood pellets, light a fire, slide in the pizza, turn it often, and enjoy delicious stone-baked pizza. Cooking outdoors with our portable outdoor pizza oven is that simple.

Details:

Description:

1.4-Pack Kids Nap Cots: These kids nap cots are perfect for preschoolers and toddlers, offering a comfy and practical napping space. These stackable nap cots meet CPSIA standards and feature rounded edges for extra sound. The tight-fitting Oxford fabric keeps little hands and feet protected while resting, so your kids can nap comfortably.
3.Comfy & Breathable: Kids can stretch out and find the perfect nap position on the durable Oxford fabric. The breathable material and 5.9 in / 15 cm raised feet help air flow freely underneath, keeping the cot clean and off the ground. This ensures a cooler, more hygienic space for kids to relax and nap.
4.Stackable & Space-Saving: These stackable sleeping daycare cots are designed to stack vertically, so you can fit up to 20 cots in a small space. They're easy to separate when it's time for a nap, and the rounded corners make it simple to lift and set up quickly-making nap time fast and efficient for both kids and caregivers.

Product Name: VEVOR Inflatable Tents for Camping, 8-12 Person Easy Setup Blow up Tent with Hand Pump, 4 Season Luxury Glamping Tent with 2 Skylights, Canopy, Stove Jack, 2 Doors & Mesh Windows (Include Storage Bag)
Description:
Highlights:
1.Excellent Ventilation: This inflatable camping tent features 2 large skylights for panoramic views and stargazing. The spacious main door opens fully, and 4 side windows ensure optimal airflow. With mesh screens to block dust and zippered doors, your blow up tent stays secure and comfortable, even at night.
2.Quick 10-15 Minute Setup: Set up your inflatable camping tent with pump in just 10-15 minutes. The high-pressure pump eliminates the need for complicated frame installations. You won't need to re-inflate for up to 48 hours, saving you time and effort. The pressure valve prevents overinflation, protecting the tent's air columns for long-lasting use.
3.186 SQ.FT. Spacious Interior: With 186 sq.ft. of space (15.75 x 11.81 x 7.22 ft / 4.8 x 3.6 x 2.2 m), this inflatable camping tent can comfortably accommodate 8-12 people. It includes removable curtains to create a two-bedroom layout or a spacious living area. Equipped with a stove jack and AC port, it's ideal for year-round use.
4.Durable & Weather-Resistant: Made with high-quality Oxford fabric, the canopy of this blow up air tent blocks harmful sunlight and has a waterproof rating of PU2000, keeping you dry during light rain. The windproof pegs and reflective guy ropes ensure security at night. The polyester cotton fabric offers comfort and breathability, preventing overheating. In case of heavy rain, please use the included waterproof canopy.
5.Compact & Easy to Carry: This blow up camping tent is compact and portable. With the included storage bag, it's easy to fold and transport. Durable zippers provide smooth operation and long-lasting performance, making it perfect for road trips, family camping, or spontaneous outdoor excursions.

Product Name: Suede Touch Gloves
Description:
Details:

Clarissa Suede Touch Gloves—a perfect blend of style, warmth, and functionality for the winter season. These women's winter gloves are designed with touchscreen technology, allowing you to easily text and use your phone without exposing your hands to the cold. Made from premium suede, they offer a luxurious feel while providing excellent protection from the wind and chilly temperatures.

The gloves feature a fleece-lined interior for added warmth and comfort, ensuring your hands stay cozy during the coldest days. Their slim cut and adjustable wrist design offer a sleek, snug fit without sacrificing mobility. Whether you're driving, running errands, or heading out for a winter stroll, these gloves are windproof and thermally insulated, keeping you comfortable in style.

Key Features:

Touchscreen-compatible fingers for easy texting
Windproof and warm with thick fleece lining
Slim cut design for a sleek, tailored fit
Made with genuine suede leather for a luxurious finish
Elastic cuff for a secure and comfortable fit
Colors: Black, Pink, Gray,Brown
